nt%20to%20their%20happiness%2C%20according%20to%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20influential%20driver%20of%20happiness%20for%20members%20of%20the%20generation%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%20in%20their%20work%20or%20school%2C%20researchers%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20important%20to%20Gen%20Z%20is%20whether%20they%20feel%20like%20their%20life%20matters%20and%20they're%20making%20a%20difference%2C%20more%20so%20than%2C%20'Am%20I%20going%20to%20work%20making%20a%20ton%20of%20money%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-rejects-promotions-management-roles-traditional-corporate-ladder-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20a%20big%20promotion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C'%20things%20like%20that%2C'%26quot%3B%20Zach%20Hrynowski%2C%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20authors%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F04%2F09%2Fhealth%2Fgen-z-happiness-gallup-wellness%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2043%25%20to%2049%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20said%20they%20don't%20feel%20like%20what%20they%20do%20each%20day%20is%20interesting%2C%20important%2C%20or%20motivating%2C%20according%20to%20the%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20previously%20reported%20on%20Gen%20Z's%20new%20approach%20to%20the%20workplace%2C%20including%20the%20generation's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-working-to-live-rather-than-living-to-work-2024-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520future%252Dof%252Dwork%2520expert%2520said%2520Gen%2520Zers%2520%2522work%2Cpersonal%2520lives%2520and%2520well%252Dbeing.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edislike%20for%20the%20standard%209%20to%205%20corporate%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20their%20tendency%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-gen-z-is-rewriting-the-rules-of-work-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeak%20their%20minds%20freely%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20workplace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Zers%20need%20to%20feel%20like%20their%20life%20is%20significant%20in%20order%20to%20achieve%20happiness%2C%20the%20study%20found%2C%20and%20perhaps%20because%20of%20this%20requirement%2C%20people%20in%20the%20age%20group%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20have%20positive%20feelings%20about%20their%20lives%20than%20members%20of%20older%20generations%20did%20at%20the%20same%20age%2C%20Hrynowski%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gallup%20study%20isn't%20a%20direct%20comparison%20but%20did%20use%20previous%20surveys%20to%20assess%20differing%20happiness%20levels%20between%20Gen%20Z%20and%20prior%20generations%2C%20Hrynowski%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdequate%20amounts%20of%20sleep%20and%20relaxation%20ranked%20second%20among%20factors%20contributing%20to%20Gen%20Z%20happiness.%20Those%20who%20get%20enough%20sleep%20each%20night%20are%20twice%20as%20likely%20to%20describe%20themselves%20as%20happy%2C%20the%20study%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20happiest%20members%20of%20the%20generation%20are%20also%20those%20most%20likely%20to%20feel%20love%20and%20support%20from%20those%20close%20to%20them.%20In%20contrast%2C%20people%20who%20compare%20themselves%20to%20others%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20feel%20frequent%20anxiety%2C%20according%20to%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20perception%20that%20Gen%20Z%20is%20really%20connected%2C%20but%20are%20those%20connections%20of%20a%20high%20quality%20in%20there%3F%20Are%20they%20giving%20you%20the%20love%20and%20the%20support%20that%20you%20really%20need%3F%26quot%3B%20Hrynowski%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F04%2F10%2Fthe-no-1-thing-that-influences-gen-zs-happiness-a-new-survey-shows.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20also%20found%20that%20members%20of%20Gen%20Z%20who%20identify%20as%20LGBTQ%2B%20are%2016%20percentage%20points%20less%20likely%20to%20say%20they%20are%20happy%20%E2%80%94%20an%20important%20data%20point%20given%20previous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F470708%2Flgbt-identification-steady.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGallup%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20found%20as%20many%20as%201%20in%205%20members%20of%20the%20age%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneration-z-cares-values-sexual-identity-queer-2023-12%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520BI%2527s%2520survey%252C%25205%2525%2520of%2Cof%2520boomers%2520identified%2520as%2520queer.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentify%20as%20queer.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-less-happy-than-previous-generations-purpose-sleep-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712800673000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66173a783f923f7dab06aa94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-less-happy-than-previous-generations-purpose-sleep-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20Gallup%20poll%20found%20that%20as%20Gen%20Z%20reaches%20adulthood%2C%20their%20happiness%20levels%20significantly%20decrease.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-less-happy-than-previous-generations-purpose-sleep-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eid%202024%3A%20Swara%20drops%20pics%20of%20daughter%20Raabiyaa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712800352000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109209639%2Cimgsize-66100.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Feid-2024-swara-bhasker-drops-unseen-pics-of-daughter-raabiyaas-first-chaand-ra