al%20investigations%20into%20his%20death%20had%20ruled%20out%20foul%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESameer%20Kamath%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20Indian-American%20student%20at%20Purdue%20University%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20a%20nature%20preserve%20in%20Indiana%20on%20February%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%202%2C%20Vivek%20Taneja%2C%20a%2041-year-old%20Indian-origin%20IT%20executive%2C%20suffered%20life-threatening%20injuries%20during%20an%20assault%20outside%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Washington.%20In%20another%20tragedy%2C%2025-year-old%20Indian%20student%20Vivek%20Saini%20was%20hammered%20to%20death%20by%20a%20homeless%20drug%20addict%20in%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spike%20in%20tragic%20deaths%20of%20Indian%20students%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20raised%20significant%20concerns%20among%20the%20Indo-American%20community%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Indian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Lakshmi%20Thalanki%20from%20Boston%2C%20who%20collected%20data%20on%20the%20deaths%20of%20more%20than%2010%20students%2C%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sudden%20surge%20of%20deaths%20among%20Indian%20students%20is%20alarming%20and%20suspicious%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20FIIDS%20submitted%20various%20recommendations%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20State%2C%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20Education%20Department%2C%20universities%2C%20student%20organisations%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Indo-American%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20sudden%20rise%20in%20suspicious%20deaths%2C%20rumours%20have%20been%20circulating%20around%20the%20Indian%20American%20community%20about%20potential%20hate%20crimes%20especially%20as%20many%20deaths%20are%20clustered%20around%20East%20and%20Midwest%20universities%2C%20especially%20in%20Cleveland%20Ohio%2C%20Illinois%20and%20Indiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20them%20fear%20that%20the%20hate%20crimes%20are%20fueled%20by%20negative%20propaganda%20against%20the%20community%2C%20FIIDS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20FIIDS%20did%20not%20find%20any%20conclusive%20facts%20to%20support%20the%20rumours%2C%20they%20may%20need%20to%20be%20investigated%20to%20timely%20address%20their%20concern%2C%20a%20media%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20origin%20students%2C%20according%20to%20Open%20Doors%20Report%20(ODR)%20are%20275k%2C%20making%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20foreign%20students%20and%20bringing%20in%20USD%209%20billion%20per%20year%20in%20terms%20of%20fees%20and%20expenses%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20recent%20increase%20in%20their%20deaths%20is%20concerning%20and%2C%20if%20not%20addressed%2C%20would%20impact%20their%20confidence%20in%20the%20safety%20of%20US%20universities%2C%20potentially%20impacting%20the%20inflow%20of%20students%20further%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Khanderao%20Kand%2C%20chief%20of%20Policies%20and%20Strategy%20at%20FIIDS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFIIDS%20also%20announced%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20survey%20of%20Indian-American%20students%20regarding%20their%20concerns%20and%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712799300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-09%2Fq35u6gic_india-us-flags-reuters_625x300_18_September_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffoundation-for-india-and-indian-diaspora-studies-appeal-to-us-government-over-indian-origin-student-deaths-5411037%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20prominent%20Indian%20expatriates'%20body%20has%20urged%20various%20agencies%20of%20the%20US%20government%2C%20universities%2C%20and%20student%20associations%20to%20work%20towards%20addressing%20the%20spike%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20Indian-origin%20students%20in%20the%20US%20in%20recent%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22