ll%20as%20Lucy%20MacLean%20in%20%26quot%3BFallout.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAmazon%20Prime%20Video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Lucy%20explores%20a%20new%20Vault%20in%20episode%20six%2C%20she%20discovers%20the%20history%20of%20how%20postapocalyptic%20America%20continued%20to%20develop%20even%20after%20the%20bombs%20dropped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20looking%20at%20a%20display%20of%20flags%20in%20a%20classroom%2C%20the%20original%20%26quot%3BFallout%26quot%3B%20theme%20music%20kicks%20in.%20It's%20a%20great%20needle%20drop%2C%20partly%20because%20it%20isn't%20overused%20or%20stuck%20into%20a%20random%20fight%20scene.%20Instead%2C%20the%20show%20saved%20it%20for%20a%20poignant%20moment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20deathclaw%20skull%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221547%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Deathclaw%20Skull%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BFallout.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616be831caec1275a6e9071%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Deathclaw%20Skull%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BFallout.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAmazon%20Prime%20Video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20final%20shots%20of%20the%20series%20sees%20Hank%20MacLean%20(Kyle%20MacLachlan)%20walking%20up%20to%20a%20monstrous%20skull%20with%20horns%20curling%20out%20of%20the%20side.%20The%20skull%20belongs%20to%20one%20of%20the%20most%20terrifying%20creatures%20in%20the%20entire%20franchise%3A%20a%20deathclaw.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20hulking%20reptilian%20beasts%20are%20notorious%20in%20the%20games%20for%20their%20aggression%20and%20can%20kill%20players%20very%20quickly%20if%20they're%20not%20at%20a%20high%20enough%20level%20or%20if%20they%20don't%20have%20powerful%20guns%20to%20take%20the%20monsters%20down.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20show%20doesn't%20intro