idor%20that%20led%20to%20their%20room.%3Cp%3EUlrike%20Lemmin-Woolfrey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20bedtime%20arrived%2C%20we%20got%20kitted%20out%20with%20huge%20sleeping%20bags%20and%20clean%20inserts%2C%20plus%20warm%20boots.%20These%20were%20all%20provided%20by%20the%20hotel.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20changing%20into%20pajamas%2C%20we%20made%20our%20way%20to%20our%20room.%20It%20was%20decked%20out%20with%20Olaf%20the%20Snowman%20from%20%26quot%3BFrozen.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrying%20to%20get%20into%20the%20sleeping%20bags%20at%20temperatures%20of%2025%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20struggle.%20But%20before%20I%20knew%20it%2C%20I%20was%20snuggling%20down%20on%20a%20solid%20block%20of%20ice%2C%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20keep%20my%20eyeballs%20warm.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20my%20life%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emy%20eyeballs%20had%20ever%20been%20cold%2C%20and%20it%20was%20an%20odd%20feeling.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20I%20put%20the%20sleeping%20bag%20over%20my%20face%2C%20and%20that%20did%20the%20trick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESleeping%20on%20a%20block%20of%20ice%20was%20surprisingly%20comfortable.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20beds%20at%20the%20Snowhotel%20Kirkenes%20in%20Norway%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660f818716bde8d4ead5f437%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20found%20sleeping%20on%20an%20ice%20bed%20surprisingly%20comfortable.%3Cp%3EUlrike%20Lemmin-Woolfrey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20turned%20our%20small%20light%20off%2C%20the%20room%20was%20dark%2C%20with%20only%20a%20bit%20of%20the%20corridor%20lights%20shining%20through%20the%20curtain.%20It%20was%20very%20quiet%2C%20with%20no%20noise%20at%20all%20coming%20through%20the%20ice%20walls.%20I%20also%20discovered%20that%20an%20ice%20bed%20has%20the%20distinct%20advantage%20of%20the%20mattress%20not%20shifting%20or%20squeaking%2C%20while%20the%20reindeer%20skins%20were%20soft%20and%20insulating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20dropped%20off%20to%20sleep%20quickly%2C%20and%2C%20for%20the%20first%20few%20hours%2C%20I%20slept%20well%2C%20surprisingly%20snugly.%20But%20then%20I%20needed%20to%20pee.%20The%20thought%20of%20getting%20out%20of%20the%20sleeping%20bag%2C%20running%20along%20the%20icy%20corridor%20into%20the%20main%20building%2C%20peeing%2C%20and%20then%20doing%20it%20all%20in%20reverse%20was%20simply%20too%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20escaped%20to%20the%20cabin%20for%20a%20bathroom%20break%20and%20a%20restful%20sleep.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20from%20the%20window%20of%20one%20of%20Snowhotel%20Kirkenes'%2010%20wooden%20chalets%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660f82703f923f7dab04ea0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20from%20one%20of%20the%20wooden%20chalets.%3Cp%3EUlrike%20Lemmin-Woolfrey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20on%20my%20boots%20and%20warm%20jacket%20and%20ran%20out%20of%20the%20snow%20hotel%20and%20into%20the%20night%2C%20where%20it%20was%20snowing%20beautifully.%20I%20ran%20across%20the%20path%20into%20the%20chalet%20my%20husband%20%E2%80%94%20already%20aware%20of%20my%20nighttime%20habits%20%E2%80%94%20had%20booked%20at%20a%20discounted%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20had%20spoken%20to%20reception%20late%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20when%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20no%20daytrippers%20or%20late%20arrivals%20were%20due%20that%20day%2C%20and%20after%20I%20had%20begun%20to%20fret%20about%20the%20bathroom%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20hotel's%20website%2C%20one%20night%20in%20a%20one-bedroom%20chalet%20in%20February%20is%20listed%20at%208%2C000%20Norwegian%20Krone%2C%20or%20%24743.%20My%20husband%20was%20able%20to%20convince%20the%20hotel%20to%20add%20this%20on%20for%20an%20extra%20%24100%20instead%2C%20as%20no%20other%20guests%20would%20be%20joining%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20peed%20in%20our%20private%20bathroom%2C%20slid%20into%20a%20real%20bed%2C%20with%20a%20real%20blanket%2C%20no%20dead%20reindeer%20or%20sleeping%20bag%20to%20battle%20with%2C%20and%20slept%20contentedly.%20And%2C%20even%20better%2C%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20I%20had%20a%20coffee%20while%20sitting%20in%20the%20window%20seat%20of%20the%20tiny%20cabin%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20outfitted%20with%20only%20a%20bed%20and%20two%20chairs%2C%20a%20coffee-making%20tray%2C%20and%20a%20shower%20room%20%E2%80%94%20soaking%20in%20the%20snowy%20landscape%20before%20heading%20across%20for%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWould%20I%20do%20it%20again%3F%20Even%20at%20a%20cheaper%20price%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20simply%20because%20I%20need%20to%20get%20up%20to%20go%20to%20the%20toilet%20every%20night.%20Otherwise%2C%20yes%2C%20I%20would.%20The%20sleep%20was%20blissful%20while%20it%20lasted.%20But%20I'd%20only%20do%20it%20for%20one%20night%2C%20then%20off%20into%20the%20chalet%20for%20the%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farctic-circle-norway-ice-hotel-snow-winter-review-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712794441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660fc3ba16bde8d4ead5f790%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farctic-circle-norway-ice-hotel-snow-winter-review-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sleeping%20on%20a%20bed%20made%20from%20ice%20had%20been%20on%20my%20bucket%20list%20for%20years.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20I%20realized%20the%20chalet%20was%20a%20better%20fit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ulrike%20Lemmin-Woolfrey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonical