caption%3EAn%20example%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BBroadband%20Facts%26quot%3B%20sheet%20for%20a%20mobile%20broadband%20plan.%3Cp%3EFederal%20Communications%20Commission%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BNutrition%20facts%26quot%3B%20style%20labels%20for%20internet%20plans%20are%20finally%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20FCC%20now%20requires%20internet%20providers%20to%20break%20down%20costs%20and%20services%20for%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FCC%20says%20the%20move%20should%20encourage%20competition%20and%20help%20consumers%20take%20charge%20of%20their%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20ever%20had%20trouble%20figuring%20out%20exactly%20what%20fees%20your%20internet%20provider%20is%20charging%20you%20and%20what%20internet%20speed%20you're%20actually%20getting%2C%20the%20FCC%20has%20your%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Communications%20Commission%20is%20now%20requiring%20internet%20providers%20to%20give%20customers%20a%20breakdown%20of%20all%20the%20costs%2C%20fees%2C%20and%20speeds%20associated%20with%20their%20plan%20in%20a%20simple%20%26quot%3Bnutrition%20facts%26quot%3B%20format%2C%20just%20like%20you%20might%20see%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20bag%20of%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeginning%20on%20April%2010%2C%20all%20internet%20companies%20that%20have%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20customers%20must%20display%20these%20labels%20at%20every%20point%20of%20sale%2C%20both%20online%20and%20in%20stores%2C%20the%20FCC%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Wednesday.%20That%20includes%20companies%20that%20provide%20both%20home%2C%20or%20fixed%2C%20internet%20services%2C%20as%20well%20as%20mobile%20broadband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProviders%20with%20fewer%20than%20100%2C000%20customers%20have%20until%20October%20to%20roll%20out%20the%20labels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20labels%20aren't%20just%20designed%20for%20new%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20internet%20service%20providers%20must%20also%20make%20them%20available%20to%20current%20customers%20in%20their%20online%20account%20portals%20and%20provide%20the%20label%20when%20a%20customer%20asks%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20the%20labels%20must%20include%20a%20variety%20of%20detailed%20information%2C%20like%20introductory%20rates%2C%20data%20allowances%2C%20contract%20length%2C%20early%20termination%20fees%2C%20and%20more.%20They%20also%20must%20include%20links%20to%20information%20about%20network%20management%20practices%20and%20privacy%20policies%2C%20the%20FCC%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBroadband%20Labels%20are%20designed%20to%20provide%20clear%2C%20easy-to-understand%2C%20and%20accurate%20information%20about%20the%20cost%20and%20performance%20of%20high-speed%20internet%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FCC%20said%20in%20its%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BThe%20labels%20are%20modeled%20after%20the%20FDA%20nutrition%20labels%20and%20are%20intended%20to%20help%20consumers%20comparison%20shop%20for%20the%20internet%20service%20plan%20that%20will%20best%20meet%20their%20needs%20and%20budget.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20labels%20have%20been%20eight%20years%20in%20the%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FCC%20first%20proposed%20the%20nutrition%20facts-style%20labels%20as%20a%20voluntary%20option%20in%202016%2C%20but%20didn't%20mandate%20them%20until%202022%20following%20an%20order%20from%20Congress%20under%20the%202021%20infrastructure%20law%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fus-mandates-new-comparison-internet-service-labels-2022-11-17%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20ISPs%20got%20ahead%20of%20the%20FCC's%20April%2010%20deadline%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiber.googleblog.com%2F2023%2F10%2Fis-your-internet-high-fiber-nutrition.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Fiber%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%3C%2Fa%3E%20ISPs%20to%20roll%20out%20the%20l