2%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eruns%20out%20of%20fuel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20missiles%20are%20much%20slower%20than%20traditional%20surface-to-air%20missiles%20and%20are%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20likely%20to%20endanger%20airborne%20fighter%20jets.%20However%2C%20the%20steady%20proliferation%20of%20these%20systems%20among%20militants%20may%20provide%20an%20entirely%20new%20capability%20for%20groups%20long%20hunted%20by%20advanced%20drones%20like%20Turkey's%20Bayraktar%20TB2.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMedium-altitude%20long-endurance%20drones%2C%20like%20those%20adopted%20by%20Turkey%2C%20are%20especially%20vulnerable%20as%20they%20have%20been%20designed%20for%20use%20in%20regions%20where%20command%20of%20the%20air%20is%20maintained%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20addition%2C%20any%20low-flying%20aviation%2C%20such%20as%20helicopters%20or%20aircraft%20coming%20in%20to%20land%20at%20remote%20bases%2C%20might%20be%20under%20increased%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYet%20this%20is%20just%20the%20start%20of%20an%20offensive-defensive%20cycle%2C%20with%20states%20adapting%20their%20drones%20with%20defense%20systems%20and%20groups%20seeking%20ever%20longer%20range%20and%20more%20powerful%20air%20defense%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERyan%20Bohl%2C%20a%20senior%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20analyst%20at%20the%20risk%20intelligence%20company%20RANE%2C%20noted%20that%20the%20358-type%20missile%20has%20had%20%26quot%3Bsome%20notable%20successes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThey%20offer%20a%20certain%20degree%20of%20flexibility%20for%20Hezbollah%2C%20untying%20their%20anti-air%20defense%20network%20from%20being%20completely%20anchored%20on%20geography%20by%20allowing%20them%20to%20loiter%20in%20the%20skies%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BStill%2C%20they%20have%20not%20yet%20demonstrated%20the%20capability%20to%20close%20the%20skies%20to%20Western%20combat%20aircraft%2C%20and%20so%20they%20must%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20hindrance%20to%20Israeli%20combat%20operations%20rather%20than%20a%20substantial%20block.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERogers%20anticipated%20that%20the%20358%20and%20similar%20loitering%20missiles%20will%20%26quot%3Blikely%20continue%20to%20be%20deployed%20widely%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20worrying%20potential%20of%20escalation%20as%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20respond%20to%20attacks%20on%20their%20military%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAs%20air%20defense%20systems%20increase%20in%20power%20and%20effectiveness%2C%20it%20will%20mark%20a%20new%20challenge%20to%20drone%20systems%20that%20have%20long%20had%20command%20of%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20a%20renewed%20age%20of%20offensive%2Fdefensive%20challenges%20and%20a%20new%20age%20of%20contested%20airspace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22963%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20Central%20Command%20handout%20shows%20one%20of%20the%20Iranian-made%20538%20loitering%20missile%20seized%20by%20the%20USS%20Forrest%20Sherman%20in%20November%202019.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616ff4b1caec1275a6ed6a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22543%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Central%20Command%20handout%20shows%20one%20of%20the%20Iranian-made%20538%20loitering%20missile%20seized%20by%20the%20USS%20Forrest%20Sherman%20in%20November%202019.%3Cp%3ECENTCOM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3E'Drone%20hunting%20drones'%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeasteye.net%2Fnews%2Fturkey-pkk-acquired-kamikaze-drones-aircraft%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20in%20March%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20speculates%20that%20Turkey's%20arch-foe%2C%20the%20Kurdistan%20Workers'%20Party%20or%20PKK%20group%2C%20may%20have%20acquired%20Iranian%20Meraj%20loitering%20missiles.%20These%20claims%20coincide%20with%20the%20PKK's%20recent%20claim%20to%20have%20shot%20down%2013%20Turkish%20drones%20over%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWith%20variants%20of%20the%20Meraj%20family%20of%20'drone%20hunting%20drones'%20documented%20in%20Iraq%2C%20it%20is%20technically%20possible%20that%20the%20PKK%20has%20obtained%20such%20systems%2C%20either%20directly%20from%20Iran%20or%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20noted%20that%20the%20most%20advanced%20Meraj%20system%2C%20the%20532%2C%20has%20a%20maximum%20altitude%20of%2012%2C000%20feet.%20Turkish%20drones%20like%20the%20Bayraktar%20TB2%20and%20Akinci%20can%20fly%20at%2040%2C000%20feet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20remains%20possible%20the%20PKK%20has%20found%20ways%20to%20smuggle%20or%20illegally%20obtain%20Iranian%20systems%2C%20it%20would%20be%20in%20limited%20quantity%20given%20that%20Tehran%20has%20its%20own%20issues%20with%20the%20PKK%20and%20little%20interest%20in%20supplying%20an%20anti-Turkish%20faction%20with%20such%20systems%20for%20fear%20of%20upsetting%20Turkish-Iranian%20relations%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThis%20seems%2C%20at%20least%20on%20the%20strategic%20level%2C%20to%20be%20far-fetched.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20PKK%20would%20require%20large%20quantities%20of%20Meraj%20loitering%20systems%20if%20it%20aims%20to%20%26quot%3Bovercome%26quot%3B%20Turkey's%20overwhelming%20%26quot%3Bdrone%20and%20logistical%20advantages%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20said.%20But%20if%20the%20group%20has%20managed%20to%20capture%20or%20smuggle%20a%20few%2C%20the%20RANE%20analyst%20anticipates%20they%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20of%20localized%2C%20tactical%20consideration%20for%20individual%20PKK-Turkey%20encounters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20constraint%20for%20non-state%20actor%20use%20is%20their%20supply%3B%20they%20need%20some%20kind%20of%20firm%20supply%20line%20to%20a%20state%20that%20manufactures%20them%20since%20few%20of%20them%20can%20be%20cobbled%20together%20in%20makeshift%20factories%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20358%20has%20proven%20capable%20of%20intercepting%20occasional%20drones%20and%20complicating%20air%20operations%2C%20they%20have%20not%20shut%20any%20airspace%20to%20American%20or%20allied%20military%20operations%20and%20are%20unlikely%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20loitering%20drones%20factor%20in%20as%20less%20of%20the%20end%20of%20Western%20air%20dominance%20in%20the%20region%20and%20more%20of%20a%20way%20for%20less%20advanced%20powers%20to%20have%20at%20least%20some%20layers%20of%20air%20defense%20against%20these%20rivals%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20could%20contrast%20with%20groups%20like%20ISIS%2C%20which%20have%20virtually%20no%20air%20defenses%20whatsoever%20and%20must%20endure%20Western%20air%20power%20in%20any%20confrontation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Iran%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20they'll%20have%20networks%20of%20air%20defenses%20that%20add%20deterrence%20to%20escalation%2C%20but%20don't%20necessarily%20block%20air%20operations%2C%20especially%20covert%20ones%20by%20stealth%20units.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrone-hunting-drones-are-already-impacting-middle-east-conflicts-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712783946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6617020d16bde8d4ead7a46