%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616f9c516bde8d4ead79ca7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20inside%20of%20the%20body%20pillow%20is%20filled%20with%20CERTIPUR-US%20shredded%20memory%20foam.%20It%20comes%20with%20extra%20fill%20as%20well.%3Cp%3ECoop%20Sleep%20Goods%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cover%20is%20made%20of%20bamboo-derived%20viscose%20rayon%20and%20a%20polyester%20blend.%20It's%20dust-mite-resistant%20and%20hypoallergenic.%20Though%20the%20whole%20pillow%20is%20machine-washable%20and%20the%20cover%20feels%20great%2C%20I%20recommend%20picking%20up%20a%2054-by-20-inch%20pillowcase%20that%20zips.%20The%20pillowcase%20will%20make%20it%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20wash%20the%20pillow%20as%20often%2C%20and%20the%20zipper%20will%20keep%20the%20pillow%20from%20escaping.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20it%20looks%20nice%20on%20your%20bed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20sleep%2C%20I%20hug%20the%20body%20pillow%20with%20my%20arms%20and%20hold%20it%20between%20my%20legs.%20It%20did%20an%20excellent%20job%20of%20reducing%20strain%20on%20my%20knees%20and%20kept%20my%20spine%20aligned.%20Unless%20I%20worked%20out%20particularly%20hard%20the%20previous%20day%2C%20I%20wake%20up%20most%20mornings%20feeling%20refreshed%20with%20my%20back%20and%20legs%20pain-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seams%20on%20the%20pillow%20appear%20to%20be%20quite%20durable.%20There%20are%20about%2015%20stitches%20per%20inch%2C%20which%20is%20pretty%20good%20and%20should%20ensure%20that%20filling%20doesn't%20escape.%20Opening%20the%20pillow%2C%20you%20can%20see%20that%20the%20seams%20are%20reinforced%20well%20with%20several%20stitched%20layers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20the%20shredded%20memory%20foam%20did%20an%20excellent%20job%20of%20breathing%20and%20not%20trapping%20heat%2C%20a%20common%20problem%20with%20solid%20memory%20foam.%20I'm%20usually%20hot%20at%20night%20and%20need%20to%20turn%20the%20thermostat%20down%20to%20sleep%2C%20but%20this%20pillow%20helped%20regulate%20my%20body%20temperature.%20Even%20when%20my%20sister-in-law%20was%20visiting%20from%20LA%20and%20insisted%20on%20cranking%20the%20thermostat%20up%2C%20the%20pillow%20provided%20a%20cool%20reprieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20everyone%20has%20different%20tastes%20in%20pillows%2C%20it's%20important%20that%20you%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20test%20a%20pillow%20out%20before%20committing%20to%20it.%20Coop%20Sleep%20Goods%20offers%20a%20100-day%2C%20no-questions-asked%20refund%20policy.%20The%20company%20even%20pays%20for%20return%20shipping.%20The%20returned%20pillow%20is%20then%20donated%20to%20charity.%20The%20pillow%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20five-year%20limited%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20problem%20that%20body%20pillows%20often%20have%20is%20that%20they%20can%20take%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20in%20the%20bed.%20My%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20larger%20than%20average%20and%20have%20sizable%20body%20pillows.%20Yet%2C%20somehow%2C%20it%20never%20seemed%20like%20the%20Coop%20Sleep%20Goods%20pillow%20was%20in%20the%20way.%20We%20sleep%20on%20a%20king-sized%20bed%20so%20it%20might%20be%20a%20different%20story%20if%20you%20sleep%20on%20a%20queen%20or%20something%20smaller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shredded%20memory%20foam%20would%20occasionally%20clump%20up%20on%20the%20ends%20leaving%20less%20support%20in%20the%20middle.%20It%20wasn't%20extreme%2C%20and%20it%20usually%20happened%20over%20the%20course%20of%20several%20nights.%20If%20you%20experience%20this%2C%20you%20can%20either%20work%20the%20filling%20to%20the%20less-filled%20areas%20or%20pop%20the%20pillow%20in%20the%20dryer%20on%20low%20heat%20for%20about%20half%20an%20hour%20to%20fluff%20back%20up.%20Coop%20recommends%20fluffing%20your%20pillow%20by%20hand%20every%20morning%2C%20but%20I%20can't%20imagine%20living%20a%20life%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pillow%20is%2