eling.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ultra's%20audio%20processing%20extends%20to%20their%20sound%20performance%2C%20which%20is%20full%2C%20detailed%2C%20and%20dynamic.%20There's%20some%20extra%20zing%20to%20the%20midrange%20and%20treble%2C%20with%20musical%20bass%20to%20round%20things%20out.%20If%20the%20sound%20gets%20too%20bold%2C%20a%20three-band%20EQ%20in%20Bose's%20Music%20app%20for%20Android%20or%20iPhone%20lets%20you%20adjust%20it%20to%20taste.%20The%20app%20also%20lets%20you%20engage%20Bose's%20Spatial%20Audio%20feature%2C%20designed%20to%20create%20a%203D%20soundstage%20from%20stereo%20sound%2C%20with%20available%20head%20tracking%20to%20anchor%20you%20in%20your%20sonic%20space.%20It's%20not%20our%20favorite%20feature%20for%20music%2C%20but%20it's%20there%20if%20you%20need%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20Beats%20Fit%20Pro%2C%20the%20QC%20Ultra's%20case%20is%20rather%20bulky%20and%20does%20not%20support%20wireless%20charging%20without%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-63518-20%26h%3Dd6fda75da177e28ba4dc84281fca2bd48c6a5c6319e4be94a6fe4b557f97ea04%26postID%3D661596de3d4b1e89043514f5%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbest-airpods-alternatives%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.bose.com%252Fp%252Faccessories-carry-cases-bags%252Fbose-wireless-charging-case-cover%252FCMWB-FQCUE_WLSCH-COVERCASE.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2450%20cover%3C%2Fa%3E%20(sold%20separately).%20That's%20tough%20to%20swallow%20at%20such%20a%20high%20price%2C%20as%20is%20the%20Ultra's%20lack%20of%20multipoint%20pairing.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20earbuds%20offer%20other%20advanced%20features%2C%20like%20a%20sonic%20test%20that%20adjusts%20the%20sound%20each%20time%20you%20put%20the%20buds%20in%2C%20as%20well%20as%20more%20standard%20offerings%20like%20in-ear%20detection%20sensors%20to%20auto-pause%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBose%20has%20also%20made%20great%20strides%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20ergonomics.%20The%20QC%20Ultra%20are%20much%20smaller%20than%20the%20original%20QuietComfort%20buds%2C%20using%20a%20blend%20of%20ear%20tips%20and%20ear%20wings%20for%20a%20stable%20and%20comfy%20fit.%20The%20controls%20are%20convenient%20and%20responsive%2C%20including%20a%20handy%20volume%20slider%20on%20the%20stem%20(again%2C%20like%20the%20AirPods%20Pro).%20The%20Ultra's%20posh%20design%20mixes%20with%20great%20sound%20and%20the%20ultimate%20in%20noise-canceling%20performance%20for%20a%20pricey%20but%20premium%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20open%20ear%5C%22%3EBest%20open%20ear%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESony's%20unique%20Linkbuds%20are%20unlike%20any%20other%20earbuds%20on%20our%20list%20and%20pretty%20much%20anything%20else%20we've%20tested.%20Instead%20of%20relying%20on%20advanced%20audio%20processing%20and%20microphones%20to%20let%20in%20or%20suppress%20sound%20from%20your%20environment%2C%20the%20Linkbuds%20have%20a%20donut-shaped%20hole%20carved%20directly%20through%20the%20center%20of%20their%20audio%20drivers%20to%20keep%20you%20fully%20aware%20of%20your%20surroundings%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20the%20Linkbuds%20uniquely%20primed%20for%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20from%20your%20daily%20job%20to%20bike%20riding%20or%20even%20skiing%2C%20where%20the%20tiny%20microphones%20in%20traditional%20earbuds%20like%20the%20AirPods%20Pro%20would%20be%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20wind.%20You'll%20hear%20all%20the%20sounds%20around%20you%2C%20coming%20through%20almost%20as%20naturally%20as%20if%20you%20weren't%20wearing%20earbuds%20at%20all%20while%20still%20enjoying%20your%20favorite%20music%20or%20podcasts.%20The%20flip%20side%20is%20that%20the%20Linkbuds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20competitors%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-63518-20%26h%3Dee6222e262ea88faf1e79e4e4dd88b4207ed26673c26caf41396fb7eee44de92%26postID%3D661596de3d4b1e89043514f5%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbest-airpods-alternatives%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FBose-Earbuds-OpenAudio-Technology-Wireless%252Fdp%252FB0CPFV77W4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBose%20Ultra%20Open%20Earbuds%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20aren't%20equipped%20to%20block%20out%20unwanted%20noises.%20Unlike%20traditional%20buds%2C%20which%20offer%20noise%20canceling%20or%20passive%20noise%20isolation%2C%20you'll%20hear%20everything%20with%20the%20Linkbuds%2C%20for%20better%20and%20for%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221758%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sony%20Linkbuds%20in%20case%20being%20held%20in%20a%20person's%20hand%20outside.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616a1071caec1275a6e7d88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221319%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESony'%20Linkbuds%20are%20a%20great%20pick%20if%20you%20want%20to%20remain%20aware%20of%20your%20surroundings.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20Linkbuds%20are%20much%20cheaper%20than%20Bose's%20option%2C%20making%20them%20more%20accessible%20as%20a%20secondary%20pair%20to%20elevate%20your%20favorite%20outdoor%20activities.%20Their%20sound%20quality%20meets%20or%20exceeds%20the%20best%20open%20earbuds%20we've%20tried%2C%20carving%20out%20relatively%20detailed%20and%20full%20sound%20with%20more%20bass%20than%20you'd%20expect%20for%20buds%20with%20holes%20in%20the%20middle.%20Call%20quality%20was%20also%20impressive%20in%20our%20testing%2C%20though%20wind%20gusts%20are%20more%20of%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buds%20offer%20decent%20water%20resistance%20and%20include%20solid%20features%20like%20auto-pause%20sensors%20and%20a%20multi-band%20EQ%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Sony's%20DSEE%20audio%20engine%20designed%20to%20upscale%20compressed%20audio.%20There's%20no%20wireless%20charging%20case%20or%20multipoint%20pairing%2C%20but%20the%20buds%20do%20have%20some%20intriguing%20extras%20like%20face-touch%20controls%20to%20go%20along%20with%20regular%20touch%20controls%20for%20ease%20of%20use%20in%20heavy%20workouts.%20Their%20light%20and%20distinctive%20design%20fits%20comfortably%20and%20stays%20put%20under%20duress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Linkbuds%20aren't%20as%20versatile%20as%20traditional%20earbuds%2C%20but%20their%20moderate%20price%20and%20polished%20design%20make%20them%20our%20favorite%20AirPods%20alternative%20in%20the%20open-ear%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20unique%20style%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20a%20unique%20style%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENothing's%20Ear%202%20are%20the%20coolest-looking%20earbuds%20we've%20ever%20tested.%20Their%20stunning%20transparent%20design%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20stylish%20rectangular%20case%2C%20looks%20like%20what%20you'd%20get%20if%20you%20mixed%20the%20AirPods%20Pro%20with%20a%20James%20Bond%20film.%20You%20can%20see%20Apple-esque%20design%20touches%20all%20over%20these%20buds%2C%20particularly%20in%20their%20bulbous%20white%20housings%2C%20but%20they%20also%20chart%20their%20own%20course%2C%20offering%20an%20even%20lighter%20design%20than%20Apple's%20top%20buds%2C%20alongside%20robust%20dust%20and%20water%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nothing%202's%20feature%20set%20also%20breaks%20away%20from%20Apple%2C%20with%20third-party%20conveniences%20like%20Google%20Fast%20Pair%20and%20Microsoft%20Swift%20Pair%20and%20distinctive%20touches%20like%20a%20voice%20that%20breathes%20in%20when%20you%20engage%20their%20transparency%20mode.%20Pinch%20commands%20make%20for%20simplified%20playback%20control%20alongside%20extras%20like%20multipoint%20pairing%2C%20a%20low-lag%20mode%20for%20gaming%2C%20and%20customizable%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nothing%202's%20default%20sound%20signature%20is%20on%20the%20sharper%20side%2C%20with%20some%20snap%20in%20the%20treble%20and%20upper%20midrange%2C%20but%20you%20can%20mellow%20things%20out%20with%20the%20in-app%20EQ%20if%20that's%20not%20your%20bag.%20Bass%20is%20balanced%20and%20precise%20without%20overwhelming%20the%20other%20frequencies.%20Noise-canceling%20is%20mid-tier%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20price.%20You%20won't%20be%20wrapped%20in%20tranquility%20like%20our%20favorite%20noise-canceling%20pairs%20provide%2C%20but%20it%20does%20a%20solid%20job%20of%20suppressing%20low-frequency%20sounds%20and%20allows%20for%20customization.%20Transparency%20mode%20is%20similarly%20effective%20at%20letting%20in%20the%20world%20around%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nothing%20Ear%202's%20biggest%20drawback%20is%20battery%20life%20that's%20stuck%20in%20the%20past.%20At%20just%20four%20hours%20with%20noise%20canceling%20(six%20hours%20without)%2C%20it's%20well%20below%20average%2C%20which%20may%20explain%20why%20the%20earbuds%20are%20so%20light%20and%20airy.%20With%20up%20to%20five%20charges%20in%20the%20case%20and%20a%20quick-charge%20feature%20for%20nearly%20two%20hours%20of%20playback%20in%2010%20minutes%2C%20it's%20mainly%20an%20issue%20for%20longer%20trips%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20noting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20this%20is%20an%20impressive%20package%20at%20a%20surprisingly%20accessible%20price%20point.%20That's%20especially%20true%20when%20you%20consider%20that%20Apple's%20standard%20AirPods%20cost%20around%20the%20same%20as%20the%20Nothing%20Ear%202%20and%20don't%20include%20options%20like%20noise%20canceling%20or%20transparency%20mode.%20It%20all%20adds%20up%20to%20a%20great%20AirPods%20alternative%2C%20with%20style%20for%20days%20and%20plenty%20of%20features%2C%20no%20matter%20your%20phone%20preference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20AirPods%20alternatives%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221758%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20a%20single%20Sony%20Linkbud%20earbud%20being%20held%20in%20a%20person's%20hand%20outside%20with%20grass%20in%20the%20b