ives%20will%20want%20to%20look%20for%20a%20consistent%20Bluetooth%20connection%20(we%20recommend%20Bluetooth%205.0%20or%20higher)%20and%20long%20battery%20life.%20Over%20five%20hours%20of%20playback%20per%20charge%20with%20ambient%20audio%20features%20engaged%20is%20solid%2C%20though%20we%20prefer%20pairs%20with%20six%20hours%20or%20more%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20refills%20in%20the%20included%20charging%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20any%20in-ear%20wireless%20earbuds%20that%20cost%20between%20%2450%20and%20%24100%20should%20include%20features%20like%20noise%20canceling%20and%20transparency%20modes%20to%20suppress%20or%20let%20in%20environmental%20audio.%20You%20should%20also%20look%20for%20earbuds%20that%20have%20dedicated%20apps%20that%20include%20options%20like%20firmware%20updates%2C%20EQ%20(equalization)%20adjustment%2C%20and%20battery%20monitoring.%20Pricier%2Fmore%20advanced%20models%20should%20typically%20include%20options%20like%20multipoint%20pairing%20to%20let%20you%20quickly%20transfer%20between%20source%20devices%20and%20a%20wireless%20charging%20case%20for%20convenient%20fill-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20most%20important%20wireless%20earbud%20factors%20are%20fit%20and%20sound%20quality.%20There's%20no%20sense%20in%20getting%20all%20those%20other%20features%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20wear%20the%20earbuds%20and%20listen%20to%20them%20long-term.%20To%20determine%20this%2C%20we%20recommend%20reading%20critical%20reviews%20and%20guides%20like%20this%20one%2C%20as%20well%20as%20user%20reviews%20on%20sites%20like%20Reddit%20and%20shopping%20sites%20like%20Amazon.%20We%20also%20recommend%20focusing%20your%20search%20on%20top%20brands%20like%20Sony%2C%20Bose%2C%20Jabra%2C%20and%20Beats.%20On%20the%20budget%20side%2C%20Anker's%20Soundcore%20line%20is%20a%20proven%20favorite.%20Whenever%20possible%2C%20we%20recommend%20trying%20earbuds%20for%20yourself%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20fit%20and%20sound%20are%20right%20for%20you%20be