ves.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Natalie%20Glaze%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20do%20a%20mad%20rush%20of%20trying%20to%20find%20electricians%20and%20plumbers%20in%20a%20very%20short%20space%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20like%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20pressure%20because%20this%20is%20a%20beautiful%20old%20house.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20make%20a%20decision%20that%20I'll%20regret%20and%20do%20something%20that%20ruins%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20like%20big%20structural%20stuff%2C%20we%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20get%20builders%20in.%26quot%3B%20But%20all%20the%20painting%2C%20the%20priming%2C%20the%20sanding%20of%20the%20floors%2C%20the%20building%20of%20wardrobes%20%E2%80%94%20we've%20done%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20keep%20the%20costs%20lower%20and%20connects%20you%20to%20a%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe're%20about%2040%25%20done%20with%20the%20renovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20cooking%20on%20the%20camping%20stove%20for%20the%20first%20six%20months%2C%20and%20there%20were%20holes%20in%20the%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20house%20is%20basically%20lath%20and%20plaster.%20It's%20super%20soft%2C%20and%20the%20ceilings%20had%20cracks%20all%20the%20way%20through.%20I%20remember%20the%20structural%20engineer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20ceilings%20are%20going%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20any%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20replaced%20four%20ceilings.%20The%20amount%20of%20dust%20when%20those%20ceilings%20came%20down%20is%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20got%20two%20fully%20finished%20rooms%3A%20the%20dressing%20room%20and%20the%20main%20bathroom.%20Then%20the%20living%20room%2C%20bedroom%2C%20and%20spare%20bedroom%20are%20part%20of%20the%20way%20there.%20They%20look%20nice%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20finished.%20Currently%20our%20kitchen%20is%20a%20building%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maintaining%20original%20features%20like%20the%20cornice%20and%20the%20baseboards%20was%20important%20to%20Glaze.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660eecbf1caec1275a6cf9df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Natalie%20Glaze%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20very%20much%20doing%20it%20room%20by%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20see%20it%20taking%20many%20years%2C%20but%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20fun.%20That%20has%20massively%20helped%20how%20overwhelming%20and%20big%20of%20a%20project%20it%20feels%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20house%20is%20full%20of%20treasures.%20When%20we%20pulled%20up%20the%20carpet%2C%20we%20found%20so%20many%20old%20newspapers%20with%20hand-drawn%20advertisements%2C%20like%20vintage%20Nivea%20adverts%20from%20the%201970s.%20I%20want%20to%20frame%20some%2C%20showcasing%20the%20house%2C%20its%20past%2C%20and%20how%20long%20it's%20been%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENinety%20percent%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20the%20downstairs%20floor%20was%20rotten.%20It%20had%20old%20woodworm%20damage.%20I%20fell%20through%20about%20five%20floorboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20were%20falling%20through%2C%20we%20found%20old%20medicine%20bottles.%20I'll%20keep%20those%20and%20display%20them%20somewhere.%20I%20love%20that%20it's%20a%20piece%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe're%20mixing%20vintage%20finds%20with%20modern%20furniture%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOld%20houses%20like%20this%20are%20so%20special.%20I%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20I'm%20honoring%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20fine%20balance%20of%20having%20the%20old%20original%20features%20%E2%80%94%20having%20vintage%20antique%20pieces%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20bringing%20in%20a%20bit%20of%20modern.%20I%20like%20to%20scour%20the%20internet%20and%20find%20stuff%20that%20I%20fall%20in%20love%20with.%20It%20can%20take%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20brought%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20old%20stuff.%20We've%20got%20a%20mirror%20on%20the%20wall%20in%20the%20living%20room%20that%20my%20dad%20bought%2035%20years%20ago%20at%20Portobello%20Market.%20It's%20come%20with%20me%20to%20every%20house%20I've%20lived%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Glaze%20esimates%20they're%20around%2040%25%20finished%20with%20the%20project.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660ee97b1caec1275a6cf792%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGlaze%20estimates%20she%20and%20her%20partner%20are%20about%2040%25%20finished%20with%20the%20renovation.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Natalie%20Glaze%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cornice%20is%20original.%20We've%20restored%20all%20the%20baseboards%20because%20they%20don't%20make%20them%20like%20that%20anymore.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20very%20important%20that%20it%20still%20feels%20like%20a%20Victorian%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20an%20old%20coal%20cellar%20in%20the%20house.%20I%20remember%20when%20I%20first%20looked%20at%20it%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BAm%20I%20going%20to%20be%20scared%20in%20this%20house%20by%20myself%3F%20Will%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-living-in-a-haunted-nyc-brownstone-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeel%20haunted%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20everyone%20who%20comes%20in%20just%20says%20this%20house%20has%20a%20lovely%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20granddaughter%20of%20the%20lady%20who%20lived%20here%20before%20us%20saw%20some%20of%20my%20TikTok%20videos.%20She%20contacted%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20whole%20family%20have%20lived%20here.%20We%20were%20so%20happy%20here.%20I'm%20so%20glad%20it's%20gone%20to%20you.%20It%20looks%20like%20you're%20taking%20care%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWho%20knows%20with%20life%20and%20circumstances%2C%20but%20I%20can%20see%20myself%20living%20here%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%20and%20being%20very%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-bought-crumbling-victorian-london-house-big-renovation-no-regrets-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712780526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660ec8013f923f7dab049eb3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-bought-crumbling-victorian-london-house-big-renovation-no-regrets-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Natalie%20Glaze%20said%20the%20house%20had%20rotten%20floors%2C%20crumbling%20walls%2C%20and%20caved-in%20ceilings.%20Renovating%20it%20is%20intense%2C%20but%20worth%20it%2C%20she%20added.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mnoyen%40insider.com%20(Maria%20Noyen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-bought-crumbling-victorian-london-house-big-renovation-no-regrets-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20says%20Arizona%20abortion%20ban%20goes%20too%20far%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712780208000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1494E%2Fproduction%2F_133120348_gettyimages-2147029843.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68783408%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20presumptive%20Republican%20presidential%20nominee%20also%20said%20he%20would%20not%20sign%20a%20federal%20abortion%20ban.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A193%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68783408%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68783408.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww