l%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20clarified%20that%20the%20amounts%20deposited%20by%20the%20DMRC%20shall%20be%20refunded%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdmrc-not-required-to-pay-rs-8-000-crore-to-reliance-infra-arm-says-sc-124041001101_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdmrc-not-required-to-pay-rs-8-000-crore-to-reliance-infra-arm-says-sc-124041001101_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdmrc-not-required-to-pay-rs-8-000-crore-to-reliance-infra-arm-says-sc-124041001101_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anil%20Ambani%20Suffers%20Another%20Setback%2C%20Group%20Firm%20Loses%20Rs%208%2C000%20Crore%20Arbitral%20Award%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20ranked%20the%20sixth%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world%20in%202008%20but%20a%20series%20of%20setbacks%20--%20the%20latest%20being%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20setting%20aside%20a%20Rs%208%2C000%20crore%20arbitral%20award%20that%20was%20granted%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20firm%20in%20his%20group%20--%20reversed%20his%20fortunes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20MBA%20from%20Wharton%20School%2C%20Anil%20Ambani%2C%2064%2C%20the%20younger%20son%20of%20legendary%20business%20tycoon%2C%20Dhirubhai%20Ambani%2C%20was%20known%20for%20his%20flamboyant%20nature%20--%20he%20married%20Bollywood%20actress%20Tina%20Munim%20and%20was%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20for%20two%20years%20--%20as%20much%20as%20for%20his%20unbeatable%20business%20acumen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20he%20has%20had%20setbacks%20across%20businesses%20that%20pushed%20him%20out%20of%20the%20billionaire%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20set%20aside%20a%20Rs%208%2C000%20crore%20arbitral%20award%20granted%20in%20favour%20of%20Delhi%20Airport%20Metro%20Express%20Pvt%20(DAMEPL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20award%20was%20in%20relation%20to%20a%20dispute%20arising%20out%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bconcession%20agreement%26quot%3B%20that%20was%20entered%20into%20between%20DAMEPL%20(a%20subsidiary%20of%20Anil%20Ambani's%20Reliance%20Infrastructure)%20and%20Delhi%20Metro%20Rail%20Corp%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20DAMEPL%20to%20refund%20all%20sums%20previously%20paid%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Metro%20Rail%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20arbitral%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMRC%20had%20paid%20Rs%203%2C300%20crore%20to%20the%20Reliance%20Infra%20arm%2C%20which%20now%20needs%20to%20be%20refunded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Ambani's%20Reliance%20Infrastructure%20Ltd%20in%20a%20stock%20exchange%20filing%20that%20no%20liability%20has%20been%20imposed%20on%20it%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReliance%20Infrastructure%20wishes%20to%20clarify%20that%20the%20Order%20dated%20April%2010%2C%202024%2C%20passed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20does%20not%20impose%20any%20liability%20on%20the%20company%20and%20the%20company%20has%20not%20received%20any%20money%20from%20DMRC%2FDAMEPL%20under%20the%20arbitral%20award%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20DAMEPL%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Reliance%20Infrastructure%2C%20it%20is%20a%20separate%20entity%20and%20the%20liability%20falls%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Dhirubhai%20suffered%20a%20stroke%20in%201986%2C%20Anil%20took%20on%20day-to-day%20management%20of%20Reliance's%20financial%20relationships%20under%20his%20father's%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20elder%20brother%2C%20Mukesh%2C%20assumed%20joint%20leadership%20of%20the%20Reliance%20companies%20after%20their%20father's%20death%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20soon%20after%20they%20feuded%20over%20control%2C%20leading%20to%20split%20--%20Mukesh%20got%20control%20of%20flagship%20oil%20and%20petrochemicals%2C%20while%20Anil%20gained%20control%20of%20the%20newer%20businesses%20such%20as%20telecommunications%2C%20power%20generation%2C%20and%20financial%20services%20through%20a%202005%20demerger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20brothers%2C%20who%20had%20diverging%20fortunes%20thereafter%2C%20did%20not%20stop%20feuding.%20They%20fought%20over%20supply%20of%20gas%20from%20fields%20operated%20by%20Mukesh's%20company%20to%20the%20power%20plant%20of%20Anil's%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elder%20brother%20won%20the%20case%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20said%20a%20family%20pact%20cannot%20override%20a%20government's%20allocation%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20borrowed%20money%20to%20fuel%20an%20expansion%20with%20forays%20into%20infrastructure%2C%20defence%2C%20and%20entertainment%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202009%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20quashed%20land%20acquisition%20for%20the%20proposed%20mega%20gas-based%20power%20project%20at%20Dadri%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20by%20Anil's%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20non-compete%20clause%20between%20the%20brothers%20kept%20Mukesh%20out%20of%20telecom%20but%20that%20was%20scrapped%20in%202010.%20Mukesh%20quickly%20returned%2C%20pumping%20in%20more%20than%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20crore%20over%20the%20next%20seven%20years%20to%20build%20a%20speedier%204G%20wireless%20network%2C%20which%20drove%20out%20competition%2C%20including%20Anil's%20Reliance%20Communications%20(RCom).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20venture%20into%20the%20entertainment%20business%20with%20a%20%241.2%20billion%20deal%20with%20Adlabs%20in%202005%20and%20DreamWorks%20in%202008%20did%20not%20work.%20In%202014%2C%20his%20power%20and%20infrastructure%20companies%20plunged%20into%20huge%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20sold%20assets%20to%20quell%20investor%20concerns%20around%20the%20indebtedness%20of%20some%20of%20his%20companies.%20He%20sold%20companies%20like%20Big%20Cinema%2C%20Reliance%20Big%20Broadcasting%2C%20and%20Big%20Magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCom%2C%20which%20ushered%20in%20a%20telecom%20revolution%20in%20the%20country%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20insolvency%20proceedings%20to%20repay%20debt.%20His%20bets%20on%20defence%20manufacturing%2C%20too%2C%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20threatened%20Anil%20Ambani%20with%20prison%20after%20Reliance%20Communications%20(RCom)%20failed%20to%20pay%20Rs%20550%20crore%20to%20Ericsson%20AB's%20Indian%20Unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20gave%20him%20a%20month%20to%20find%20the%20funds%20and%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20bailed%20him%20out%20at%20the%20last%20moment%20by%20giving%20the%20required%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20three%20Chinese%20banks%20dragged%20Anil%20Ambani%20to%20a%20London%20court%20over%20a%20%24680%20million%20loan%20default.%20Industrial%20%26amp%3B%20Commercial%20Bank%20of%20China%20Ltd%2C%20China%20Development%20Bank%20and%20the%20Export-Import%20Bank%20of%20China%20had%20in%202012%20agreed%20to%20loan%20%24925%20million%20to%20his%20group%20firm%20Reliance%20Communications%20on%20condition%20that%20he%20provide%20a%20personal%20guarantee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCom%20defaulted%20and%20the%20three%20banks%20sued%20Ambani%2C%20who%20said%20he%20agreed%20to%20give%20a%20non-binding%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20comfort%20letter%26quot%3B%20but%20never%20a%20guarantee%20tied%20to%20his%20personal%20assets.%20The%20matter%20is%20still%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReliance%20Capital%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20in%202021%20after%20defaulting%20on%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2024%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReliance%20Infrastructure%20Ltd%2C%20which%20built%20Mumbai's%20first%20metro%20line%2C%20missed%20a%20bond%20payment%20as%20it%20waited%20for%20proceeds%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20power%20transmission%20assets%20to%20Gautam%20Adani's%20unit%20to%20cover%20the%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is