ose%20to%20the%20ED)%2C%20during%20the%20course%20of%20a%20legal%20meeting.%20It%20thus%20appears%20that%20the%20applicant%20is%20not%20even%20utilizing%20the%20permitted%20two%20legal%20interviews%20per%20week%20with%20his%20counsels%20solely%20for%20discussing%20his%20pending%20litigations%20and%20has%20rather%20used%20the%20allotted%20time%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20legal%20interviews%20in%20the%20aforesaid%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20cited%20a%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20judgment%2C%20which%20said%20every%20citizen%20of%20India%20is%20entitled%20to%20protection%20of%20law%2C%20which%20will%20also%20equally%20apply%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20dismissed%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20submission%20that%20about%2035%20cases%20were%20pending%20against%20him%20across%20the%20country%20for%20which%20he%20needed%20more%20time%20with%20his%20lawyer%20for%20consultation%2C%20saying%20his%20application%20was%20bereft%20of%20necessary%20details%20of%20cases%2C%20including%20their%20number%2C%20the%20nature%20and%20stage%20of%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%2C%20in%20the%20course%20of%20arguments%2C%20it%20was%20submitted%20by%20counsel%20for%20applicant%20that%20there%20are%20about%2030-35%20litigations%20regarding%20which%20the%20applicant%20needs%20to%20have%20consultations%20and%20discussions%20with%20his%20counsels%2C%20but%2C%20there%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20any%20objective%20criteria%20for%20assessing%20if%20five%20meetings%20with%20his%20lawyers%20per%20week%20would%20be%20sufficient%20to%20address%20the%20concern%20of%20the%20applicant%20or%20that%20two%20meetings%2C%20which%20are%20permitted%20as%20per%20jail%20rules%2C%20are%20insufficient%20for%20this%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20such%20objective%20criteria%20for%20assessment%2C%20the%20prayer%20of%20the%20applicant%20for%20five%20legal%20interviews%20with%20his%20lawyers%20per%20week%20not%20only%20appears%20to%20be%20whimsical%20but%20also%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20made%20without%20any%20statistical%20basis%20or%20objective%20standards%20for%20assessment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20opposed%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20application%2C%20saying%20special%20privileges%20cannot%20be%20extended%20to%20him%20merely%20because%20he%20wants%20to%20run%20the%20government%20from%20inside%20the%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20alleged%20that%20legal%20interviews%20were%20being%20misused%20by%20Kejriwal%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20issued%20some%20instructions%20on%20matters%20related%20to%20governance%20from%20jail%20and%20his%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20asserted%20he%20will%20run%20the%20government%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712772780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4t8b8ev8_arvind-kejriwal-ani-650_650x400_04_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-gave-orders-to-atishi-from-jail-through-lawyers-delhi-court-5414224%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Delhi%20court%20on%20Wednesday%20dismissed%20an%20application%20moved%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20arrested%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20seeking%20more%20time%20with%20his%20lawyers%20and%20said%20relevant%20rules%20are%20equally%20applicable%20to%20him%20and%20other%20inmates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-gave-orders-to-atishi-from-jail-through-lawyers-delhi-court-5414224%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs