0economic%20turmoil.%20This%20upheaval%20had%20a%20surprising%20consequence%3A%20a%20delayed%20return%20for%20Krikalev%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Flessons-from-history%2Fthe-last-soviet-citizen-sergei-krikalevs-forgotten-odyssey-in-space-f70a4bf5c28d%5C%22%3Enews%20outlet.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFunding%20constraints%20and%20a%20disrupted%20cosmonaut%20rotation%20programme%20meant%20Krikalev%20spent%20an%20unintended%2010%20months%20in%20space%2C%20a%20record-breaking%20feat.%20While%20the%20cosmonaut%20maintained%20his%20usual%20routine%20onboard%20Mir%2C%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20his%20return%20loomed%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D476%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fupsocltheenigma%252Fvideos%252F392529506887691%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D476%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22476%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22476%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extended%20stay%20presented%20challenges.%20Microgravity%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20Krikalev's%20physical%20health%2C%20leading%20to%20muscle%20and%20bone%20weakening.%20Social%20isolation%20and%20disrupted%20communication%20from%20a%20changing%20Earth%20added%20to%20the%20psychological%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20after%2010%20months%20and%205%2C000%20Earth%20orbits%2C%20Krikalev%20returned%20to%20a%20completely%20different%20world.%20The%20Soviet%20Union%20was%20gone%2C%20replaced%20by%20newly%20independent%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReadapting%20to%20Earth's%20gravity%20proved%20difficult%2C%20requiring%20extensive%20physical%20therapy.%20The%20social%20and%20political%20landscape%20Krikalev%20left%20behind%20had%20vanished%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESergei%20Krikalev's%20space%20mission%20wasn't%20just%20about%20scientific%20research.%20He%20became%20a%20global%20symbol%20of%20human%20connection%2