0India%20and%20China%20are%20important%20for%20the%20entire%20region%20and%20the%20world%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20expressed%20hope%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20will%20be%20able%20to%20restore%20and%20sustain%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20at%20their%20borders%20through%20positive%20and%20constructive%20bilateral%20engagement%20at%20the%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2F2024%2F04%2F19%2Fexclusive-interview-narendra-modi-unstoppable-rise-india-1888678.html%5C%22%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20US's%20Newsweek%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20relationship%20with%20China%20is%20important%20and%20significant%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20my%20belief%20that%20we%20need%20to%20urgently%20address%20the%20prolonged%20situation%20on%20our%20borders%20so%20that%20the%20abnormality%20in%20our%20bilateral%20interactions%20can%20be%20put%20behind%20us.%20Stable%20and%20peaceful%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20China%20are%20important%20for%20not%20just%20our%20two%20countries%20but%20the%20entire%20region%20and%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20and%20believe%20that%20through%20positive%20and%20constructive%20bilateral%20engagement%20at%20the%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20levels%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20restore%20and%20sustain%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20our%20borders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20wide-ranging%20interview%20with%20the%20New%20York-based%20magazine%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20talked%20about%20a%20host%20of%20issues%20including%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20ties%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20Quad%2C%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20and%20democracy%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20ties%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20he%20congratulated%20his%20Pakistani%20counterpart%20when%20he%20took%20charge%20and%20asserted%20that%20India%20has%20always%20advocated%20for%20advancing%20peace%2C%20security%2C%20and%20prosperity%20in%20the%20region%20in%20an%20atmosphere%20free%20from%20terror%20and%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20imprisonment%20of%20former%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20won't%20comment%20on%20matters%20internal%20to%20Pakistan.%26quot%3B%20Talking%20about%20China%20and%20the%20Quad%20grouping%2C%20he%20said%20the%20US%2C%20Australia%2C%20Japan%2C%20India%2C%20and%20China%20are%20members%20of%20many%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20present%20in%20different%20combinations%20in%20different%20groups.%20Quad%20is%20not%20aimed%20against%20any%20country.%20Like%20many%20other%20international%20groupings%2C%20like%20SCO%2C%20BRICS%2C%20and%20others%2C%20Quad%20is%20also%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20countries%20working%20on%20a%20shared%20positive%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Quad%20grouping%20comprises%20India%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Australia%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20criticism%20of%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20special%20status%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20encourage%20you%20to%20visit%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20witness%20firsthand%20the%20sweeping%20positive%20changes%20happening%20on%20the%20ground.%20Do%20not%20go%20by%20what%20I%20or%20others%20tell%20you.%20I%20went%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20just%20last%20month.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20people%20have%20a%20new%20hope%20in%20their%20lives.%20The%20process%20of%20development%2C%20good%20governance%2C%20and%20empowerment%20of%20the%20people%20is%20to%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20believed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20reaping%20the%20peace%20dividend%3A%20over%2021%20million%20tourists%20visited%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%202023.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20decline%20in%20terror%20incidents.%20Organized%20bandh%2Fhartals%20(protests)%2C%20stone%20pelting%2C%20which%20once%20disrupted%20normal%20life%2C%20are%20now%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20newly-inaugurated%20Ram%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20he%20said%20the%20name%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20is%20imprinted%20on%20India's%20national%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20(Lord%20Ram)%20life%20has%20set%20the%20contours%20of%20thoughts%20and%20values%20in%20our%20civilization.%20His%20name%20echoes%20across%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20our%20sacred%20land.%20Therefore%2C%20during%20the%2011-day%20special%20ritual%20I%20observed%2C%20I%20made%20a%20pilgrimage%20to%20the%20places%20that%20carry%20the%20footprints%20of%20Shri%20Ram.%20The%20journey%20that%20took%20me%20to%20various%20corners%20of%20the%20country%20showed%20the%20revered%20place%20Shri%20Ram%20holds%20within%20each%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20return%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20to%20his%20birthplace%20marked%20a%20historic%20moment%20of%20unity%20for%20the%20nation.%20It%20was%20a%20culmination%20of%20centuries%20of%20perseverance%20and%20sacrifice.%20When%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20ceremony%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20would%20be%20representing%201.4%20billion%20people%20of%20the%20country%20who%20have%20waited%20patiently%20for%20centuries%20to%20witness%20Ram%20Lalla's%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%2011%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20this%20auspicious%20event%2C%20I%20carried%20with%20me%20the%20aspirations%20of%20countless%20devotees%2C%20eagerly%20anticipating%20this%20day.%20The%20ceremony%20itself%20brought%20the%20nation%20together%20into%20a%20celebration%2C%20akin%20to%20a%20second%20Diwali.%20Every%20home%20was%20illuminated%20by%20the%20light%20of%20Ram%20Jyoti.%20I%20see%20it%20as%20a%20divine%20blessing%20that%20I%20could%20experience%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20as%20a%20representative%20of%201.4%20billion%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20his%20government%20has%20an%20excellent%20track%20record%20of%20fulfilling%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20second%20term%2C%20even%20the%20most%20popular%20governments%20start%20losing%20support.%20Discontent%20toward%20governments%20has%20also%20increased%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20in%20the%20world.%20India%20stands%20out%20as%20an%20exception%2C%20where%20popular%20support%20for%20our%20government%20is%20increasing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20India%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mother%20of%20democracy%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20that%20as%20the%20largest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20over%20600%20million%20people%20voted%20in%20the%20general%20elections%20in%202019%20and%20in%20a%20few%20months%20from%20now%2C%20over%20970%20million%20eligible%20voters%20will%20exercise%20their%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%20one%20million%20polling%20stations%20would%20be%20set%20up%20across%20India.%20Constantly%20increasing%20voter%20participation%20is%20a%20big%20certificate%20for%20the%20people's%20faith%20in%20Indian%20democracy.%20A%20democracy%20like%20India%20can%20move%20ahead%20and%20function%20only%20because%20there%20is%20a%20vibrant%20feedback%20mechanism.%20And%20our%20media%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20this%20regard.%20We%20have%20around%201.5%20lakh%20(150%2C000)%20registered%20media%20publications%20and%20hundreds%20of%20news%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712765220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fpm-mo