content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20sons%20of%20Hamas%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20in%20Gaza%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20Islamist%20group%20and%20Haniyeh's%20family%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20sons%20-%20Hazem%2C%20Amir%20and%20Mohammad%20-%20were%20killed%20after%20the%20car%20they%20were%20driving%20in%20was%20bombed%20in%20Gaza's%20Al-Shati%20camp%2C%20Hamas%20said.%20Two%20of%20Haniyeh's%20grandchildren%20were%20also%20killed%20in%20the%20attack%20and%20a%20third%20was%20wounded%2C%20Hamas%20media%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20demands%20are%20clear%20and%20specific%20and%20we%20will%20not%20make%20concessions%20on%20them.%20The%20enemy%20will%20be%20delusional%20if%20it%20thinks%20that%20targeting%20my%20sons%2C%20at%20the%20climax%20of%20the%20negotiations%20and%20before%20the%20movement%20sends%20its%20response%2C%20will%20push%20Hamas%20to%20change%20its%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20Haniyeh%20told%20pan-Arab%20Al%20Jazeera%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20blood%20of%20my%20sons%20is%20not%20dearer%20than%20the%20blood%20of%20our%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Haniyeh%2C%20who%20is%20based%20abroad%20in%20the%20Gulf%20Arab%20state%20of%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaniyeh%20has%20been%20the%20tough-talking%20face%20of%20Hamas'%20international%20diplomacy%20as%20war%20with%20Israel%20has%20raged%20back%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20where%20his%20family%20home%20was%20destroyed%20in%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20back%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20it%20was%20studying%20an%20Israeli%20ceasefire%20proposal%20but%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bintransigent%26quot%3B%20and%20did%20not%20meet%20any%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20seventh%20month%20of%20a%20war%20in%20which%20Israel's%20air%20and%20ground%20offensive%20has%20devastated%20Gaza%2C%20Hamas%20wants%20an%20end%20to%20Israeli%20military%20operations%20and%20a%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20enclave%2C%20and%20permission%20for%20displaced%20Palestinians%20to%20return%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaniyeh's%20eldest%20son%20confirmed%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20that%20his%20three%20brothers%20were%20killed.%20%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20God%20who%20honoured%20us%20by%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20my%20brothers%2C%20Hazem%2C%20Amir%20and%20Mohammad%20and%20their%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Abdel-Salam%20Haniyeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppointed%20to%20the%20group's%20top%20job%20in%202017%2C%20Haniyeh%20has%20moved%20between%20Turkey%20and%20Qatar's%20capital%20Doha%2C%20avoiding%20Israeli-imposed%20travel%20restrictions%20in%20blockaded%20Gaza%20and%20enabling%20him%20to%20act%20as%20a%20negotiator%20in%20the%20latest%20ceasefire%20negotiations%2C%20or%20communicate%20with%20Hamas'%20main%20ally%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20regards%20the%20entire%20Hamas%20leadership%20as%20terrorists%2C%20accusing%20Haniyeh%20and%20other%20leaders%20of%20continuing%20to%20%26quot%3Bpull%20the%20strings%20of%20the%20Hamas%20terror%20organisation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20much%20Haniyeh%20knew%20about%20the%20Oct.%207%20cross-border%20attack%20on%20Israel%20by%20Gaza-based%20operatives%20beforehand%20is%20not%20clear.%20The%20attack%20plan%2C%20drawn%20up%20by%20the%20Hamas%20military%20council%20in%20Gaza%2C%20was%20such%20a%20closely%20guarded%20secret%20that%20some%20Hamas%20officials%20abroad%20seemed%20shocked%20by%20its%20timing%20and%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712764380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffvhjo22o_ismail-haniyeh_625x300_20_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F3-sons-2-grandchildren-of-hamas-chief-killed-in-israeli-airstr