ng%20the%20water%20supply.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-people-in-karachi-continue-to-face-acute-water-shortages-amid-eid-ul-fitr-celebrations%2Farticleshow%2F109201598.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-people-in-karachi-continue-to-face-acute-water-shortages-amid-eid-ul-fitr-celebrations%2Famp_articleshow%2F109201598.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-people-in-karachi-continue-to-face-acute-water-shortages-amid-eid-ul-fitr-celebrations%2Famp_articleshow%2F109201598.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Woman%20Undergoes%20Chemotherapy%20Only%20To%20Find%20Out%20She%20Never%20Had%20Cancer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Texas%20mother%20of%20two%20is%20recovering%20after%20enduring%20a%20harrowing%20ordeal.%20Lisa%20Monk%2C%2039%2C%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20rare%20form%20of%20blood%20vessel%20cancer%20in%20early%202023.%20After%20receiving%20the%20devastating%20news%2C%20Ms.%20Monk%20underwent%20gruelling%20chemotherapy%20treatments%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%20However%2C%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20into%20her%20treatment%2C%20a%20shocking%20revelation%20came%20to%20light%3A%20Ms%20Monk%20never%20had%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Monk's%20ordeal%20began%20with%20stomach%20pains.%20A%20scan%20revealed%20a%20mass%20on%20her%20spleen%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20battery%20of%20tests.%20Doctors%20delivered%20the%20life-altering%20diagnosis%20of%20angiosarcoma.%20Facing%20a%20limited%20future%2C%20Ms.%20Monk%20wrote%20letters%20to%20her%20loved%20ones%2C%20preparing%20for%20a%20future%20she%20feared%20she%20wouldn't%20see%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F04%2F09%2Fmum-underwent-chemo-terminal-cancer-find-wasnt-sick-20612863%2F%3Fito%3Darticle.app.share.top.whatsapp%5C%22%3Enews%20report.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20doctor%20told%20me%20it%20was%20cancer%2C%20I%20went%20into%20shock.%20The%20diagnosis%20was%20horrible%2C%20and%20%5Bthey%5D%20told%20me%20it%20was%20terminal%2C%26quot%3B%20recalls%20Lisa%2C%20a%20higher%20education%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20go%20home%20and%20tell%20my%20two%20kids.%20I%20didn't%20tell%20them%20at%20this%20point%20that%20it%20was%20terminal%20or%20that%20I%20only%20had%2015%20months%3B%20I%20just%20told%20them%20it%20was%20bad%2C%20but%20I%20was%20going%20to%20try%20to%20fight%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferred%20to%20a%20cancer%20hospital%2C%20Ms%20Monk%20started%20chemotherapy%20in%20March.%20The%20treatment%20took%20a%20heavy%20toll%2C%20causing%20hair%20loss%2C%20severe%20nausea%2C%20and%20weakness.%20But%20her%20world%20turned%20upside%20down%20just%20weeks%20into%20the%20second%20round.%20A%20review%20of%20her%20pathology%20report%20revealed%20a%20critical%20error%3A%20Ms.%20Monk%20did%20not%20have%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20has%20left%20Ms%20Monk%20shaken%20but%20relieved.%20The%20cause%20of%20the%20misdiagnosis%20and%20the%20next%20steps%20for%20Ms%20Monk%20remain%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20the%20nurse%20practitioner%20first%2C%20and%20she%20just%20asked%20me%20about%20my%20symptoms%2C%20and%20she%20was%20scrolling%20on%20the%20computer%20while%20she%20was%20talking%20to%20me.%20All%20of%20sudden%20she%20just%20stops%20talking%20and%20has%20this%20look%20on%20her%20face.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20turned%20to%20me%20and%20looked%20completely%20horrified%20and%20told%20me%20she%20needed%20to%20get%20the%20doctor%20and%20then%20ran%20out%20of%20the%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Lisa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20left%20me%20alone%20for%20about%2015%20minutes%2C%20and%20the%20doctor%20came%20back%20in.%20He%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20medical%20lingo%20to%20me%20and%20then%20told%20me%20I%20didn't%20have%20cancer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20confused%2C%20as%20they%20were%20acting%20like%20it%20was%20a%20bad%20thing.%20I%20just%20thought%20%5Bif%20I%20didn't%20have%20cancer%5D%20it%20meant%20the%20chemotherapy%20was%20working.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712762280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F3b4u10n8_lisa-monk_625x300_10_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-undergoes-chemotherapy-only-to-find-out-she-never-had-cancer-5414539%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lisa%20Monk%2C%20a%20Texas%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20endured%20a%20harrowing%20ordeal%20after%20being%20misdiagnosed%20with%20a%20rare%20form%20of%20blood%20vessel%20cancer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-undergoes-chemotherapy-only-to-find-out-she-never-had-cancer-5414539%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-undergoes-chemotherapy-only-to-find-out-she-never-had-cancer-5414539%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-undergoes-chemotherapy-only-to-find-out-she-never-had-cancer-5414539%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20T20%20WC%20Nears%2C%20BCCI%20Selector%20Says%20If%20Kohli%20%26quot%3BPuts%20Forward%20Certain...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20fitness%20blueprint%20designed%20by%20Virat%20Kohli%20has%20had%20a%20ripple%20effect%20on%20the%20whole%20Indian%20cricketing%20ecosystem%2C%20said%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20who%20has%20called%20MS%20Dhoni%20a%20pure%20instinct%20man%20of%20a%20sport%20that%20had%20embraced%20the%20use%20of%20data%20and%20insight%20long%20ago.%20Kohli%20might%20be%2035%20years%20old%20but%20he%20remains%20second%20to%20none%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20performing%20the%20most%20difficult%20fitness%20drills.%20%26quot%3BYou%20look%20at%20guys%20like%20Virat%20(Kohli)%2C%20he%20is%20one%20of%20those%20guys%20who%20set%20the%20benchmark.%2010-15%20years%20into%20his%20career%2C%20he%20has%20only%20got%20fitter%2C%20you%20can%20see%20the%20results.%20If%20someone%20like%20him%20sets%20an%20example%20and%20puts%20forward%20certain%20things%20that%20you%20need%20or%20certain%20fitness%20levels%20that%20you%20need%2C%20gradually%20it%20progresses%20across%20the%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGradually%20it%20has%20progressed%20(to%20the%20younger%20generation).%20The%20one%20difference%20you%20have%20seen%20over%20the%20last%2015-20%20years%20or%20so%20is%20the%20fitness%20levels%20of%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Agarkar%20on%20SportifywithPRG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20has%20been%20in%20sublime%20form%20in%20the%20ongoing%20edition%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%20smashing%20a%20record-extending%20eighth%20century%20in%20the%20tournament%20over%20the%20years%2C%20while%20also%20leading%20the%20run%20charts%20with%20316%20from%20five%20games%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni's%20instincts%20have%20seen%20him%20win%20five%20coveted%20IPL%20titles%2C%20and%20though%20he%20has%20relinquished%20the%20position%20of%20skipper%20at%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20his%20presence%20on%20the%20field%20is%20enough%20to%20infuse%20loads%20of%20confidence%20in%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20India%20cricketer%20felt%20that%20artificial%20intelligence%20cannot%20be%20a%20substitute%20to%20someone%20like%20Dhoni%20whose%20captaincy%20instincts%20are%20incredible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20data%20that's%20available%2C%20is%20incredible.%20You%20can%20plan%20a%20whole%20innings%20and%20I%20think%20everybody%20does%20it%20now%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20will%20work%20all%20the%20time.%20You%20need%20a%20captain%20on%20the%20ground%20because%20not%20everything%20that%20you've%20planned%20is%20going%20to%20go%20your%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20a%20particular%20day%20it%20might%2C%20but%20most%20days%20it%20won't.%20And%20that's%20where%20you%20need%20human%20instinct.%20That's%20why%20you%20call%20MS%20Dhoni%20a%20great%20captain%20because%20he%20had%20a%20feel%20for%20the%20game.%20He%20knew%20what%20was%20happening%20and%20how%20the%20game%20was%20changing%2C%26quot%3B%20opined%20the%2046-year-old%20former%20India%20pace%20bowler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgarkar%20said%20that%20the%20IPL%20had%20become%20a%20huge%20platform%20to%20spot%20talent%20but%20what%20mattered%20most%20was%20a%20strong%20temperament%2C%20which%20would%20set%20them%20apart%20from%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20it%2C%20(IPL)%20keeps%20throwing%20up%20players%20out%20of%20the%20blue.%20Having%20been%20a%20selector%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20players%20who%20suddenly%20come%20and%20show%20even%20on%20the%20big%20stage.%20IPL%20is%20a%20fairly%20big%20stage%20because%20of%20the%20pressures%20involved%2C%20big%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20be%20bowling%20to%20the%20top%20batters%20in%20the%20world%2C%20or%20you%20might%20be%20facing%20one%20of%20the%20top%20bowlers%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20you%20stand%20up%20and%20that's%20where%20you%20judge%20the%20temperament%20of%20a%20player%2C%20whether%20he%20can%20do%20it%20consistently%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Agarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20sometimes%20a%20difficult%20task%20because%20of%20the%20sheer%20numbers%20(of%20players%20coming%20through%20the%20domestic%20structure)%20that%20we%20have.%20But%2C%20eventually%2C%20the%20more%20you%20watch%20players%20and%20temperament%20sometimes%20separates%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgarkar%20believes%20a%20tight-knit%20side%20will%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20be%20a%20winning%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20tight-knit%20group%20generally%20helps.%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20the%20best%20friends%20but%20you%20want%20to%20enjoy%20each%20others'%20success.%20If%20that%20doesn't%20happen%20sometimes%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712762100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fj8t1i0k8_virat-kohli-afp_625x300_26_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fas-t20-world-cup-nears-bcci-chief-selector-ajit-agarkar-says-if-virat-kohli-puts-forward-certain-5413215%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fitness%20blueprint%20designed%20by%20Virat%20Kohli%20has%20had%20a%20ripple%20effect%20on%20the%20whole%20Indian%20cricketing%20ecosystem%2C%20said%20BCCI%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20Ajit%20Agarkar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Summer%20airfares%20on%20major%20domestic%20routes%20increase%20by%2013%25%2C%20shows%20data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712761800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F10%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1699593179-0765.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fsummer-airfares-on-major-domestic-routes-increase-by-13-shows-data-124041001070_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22However%2C%20the%20data%20also%20shows%20that%20summer%20airfares%20on%20key%20routes%20such%20as%20Delhi-Leh%20and%20Delhi-Kolkata%20have%20significantly%20decreased%20due%20to%20the%20introduction%20of%20new%20flights%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3