20Jaishankar%20On%20Katchatheevu%20Island%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Wednesday%20slammed%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%2C%20saying%20the%20party%20was%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20the%20Katchatheevu%20island%20issue%20from%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20event%20in%20Bikaner%2C%20Rajasthan%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20EAM%20Jaishankar%20answered%20a%20question%20on%20the%20Katchatheevu%20island%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20DMK%20is%20telling%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20that%20they%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20in%20this%20matter%20and%20blaming%20the%20central%20government%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...We%20want%20to%20make%20the%20public%20understand%20what%20DMK%20is%20telling%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20that%20they%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20in%20this%20matter%20and%20blamed%20the%20central%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20exposing%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20DMK%20was%20involved%20in%20it%20from%20the%20start%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20discussions%20were%20held%20behind%20closed%20doors%20the%20then%20DMK%20chief%20minister%20agreed%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20talks%20were%20happening%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%20an%20agreement%20happened%20and%20the%20then%20DMK%20chief%20minister%20agreed%20to%20it...The%20people%20should%20know%20that%20there%20are%20parties%20who%20say%20something%20in%20Parliament%20and%20decide%20something%20else%20behind%20closed%20doors...%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20he%20highlighted%20that%20the%20country's%20first%20prime%20minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20said%20that%20nobody%20lives%20in%20Aksai%20Chin%2C%20stressing%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20no%20attachment%20to%20India's%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecondly...Pandit%20Nehru%20had%20said%20nobody%20lives%20in%20Aksai%20Chin%20and%20nothing%20grows%20in%20Aksai%20Chin...This%20is%20their%20(Congress)%20mentality%20about%20India's%20land...They%20don't%20have%20any%20attachment%20to%20India's%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decades-old%20territorial%20and%20fishing%20rights%20dispute%20around%20Katchatheevu%20Island%20is%20in%20the%20limelight%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20opposition%20engaged%20in%20a%20war%20of%20words%20over%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20island%2C%20located%20between%20Rameswaram%20in%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20is%20traditionally%20used%20by%20both%20Sri%20Lankan%20and%20Indian%20fishermen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201974%2C%20the%20then%20central%20government%20accepted%20Katchatheevu%20as%20Sri%20Lankan%20territory%20under%20the%20%26quot%3BIndo-Sri%20Lankan%20Maritime%20Agreement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20DMK%20over%20the%20Katchatheevu%20island%20issue.%20He%20said%20that%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bcallously%26quot%3B%20gave%20away%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20alleged%20the%20ruling%20party%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20did%20%26quot%3Bnothing%26quot%3B%20to%20safeguard%20the%20state's%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712758140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F915jrebo_s-jaishankar-pti_625x300_01_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdmk-involved-in-it-from-start-s-jaishankar-on-katchatheevu-island-row-5414055%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Wednesday%20slammed%20the%20Dravida%20Munn