na%20Nikolova%20(38)%2C%20Stoyan%20Stoyanov%20(27)%2C%20Tsvetka%20Todorova%20(52)%2C%20Gyunesh%20Ali%20(33)%2C%20and%20Patritsia%20Paneva%20(26)%2C%20all%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20charges%20of%20fraud%20and%20money%20laundering%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F04%2F10%2Fbulgarian-fraud-gang-stole-54-million-uks-biggest-benefit-scam-20618763%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Enews%20outlet.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20operation%20involved%20making%20thousands%20of%20fraudulent%20Universal%20Credit%20claims%20over%20a%20five-year%20period%20(October%202016-2021).%20They%20used%20a%20variety%20of%20methods%20to%20deceive%20the%20system%2C%20including%20creating%20fake%20identities%20and%20submitting%20forged%20documents%20such%20as%20tenancy%20agreements%2C%20payslips%2C%20and%20letters%20from%20landlords%2C%20employers%2C%20and%20even%20GPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20determined%20gang%20wouldn't%20give%20up%20on%20rejected%20claims%2C%20resubmitting%20them%20persistently%20until%20they%20were%20approved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20discovered%20%26quot%3Bbenefit%20factories%26quot%3B%20set%20up%20in%20London%2C%20acting%20as%20fronts%20for%20the%20criminal%20activity.%20These%20businesses%20posed%20as%20legitimate%20agencies%20assisting%20people%20with%20obtaining%20National%20Insurance%20numbers%20and%20their%20rightful%20benefits.%20However%2C%20after%20applicants%20submitted%20their%20claims%2C%20they%20were%20essentially%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20gang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20further%20revealed%20a%20money%20laundering%20scheme%20used%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20stolen%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20details%20of%20the%20sentencing%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20announced.%20This%20case%20highlights%20a%20significant%20vulnerability%20in%20the%20benefits%20system%20and%20serves%20as%20a%20warning%20for%20stricter%20measures%20to%20prevent%20future%20large-scale%20frauds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%