er%20of%20the%20central%20agencies%20and%20his%20house%20was%20searched%20last%20year%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20corruption%20case%2C%20the%20party%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Anand%20resigned%20from%20the%20cabinet%20and%20the%20quit%20the%20party%20earlier%20today.%20%26quot%3BI%20joined%20AAP%20after%20seeing%20its%20strong%20message%20on%20fighting%20corruption.%20Today%2C%20the%20party%20has%20found%20itself%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20corrupt%20practices.%20That's%20why%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20quit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20leader%2C%20who%20handled%20the%20social%20welfare%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20hit%20rewind.%20Senior%20AAP%20leader%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20said%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20raided%20Raaj%20Kumar%20Anand's%20house%20for%2023%20hours%20in%20November.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20BJP%20was%20then%20saying%20that%20Raaj%20Kumar%20Anand%20is%20corrupt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20that%20the%20BJP's%20intention%20behind%20the%20arrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20to%20break%20AAP%2C%20Mr%20Bhardwaj%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEvery%20minister%20and%20MLA%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20is%20facing%20a%20test%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20some%20people%20will%20retreat%20in%20this%20fight%2C%20some%20will%20have%20weak%20morale%2C%20some%20will%20break%20but%20there%20are%20a%20large%20number%20of%20people%20who%20will%20face%20these%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhardwaj%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Anand's%20house%20was%20searched%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20customs-linked%20money%20laundering%20case%20in%20November%202023.%20The%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%2C%20in%20a%20complaint%20to%20a%20local%20court%2C%20had%20alleged%20false%20declarations%20in%20imports%20for%20customs%20evasions%20of%20over%20Rs%207%20crore.%20The%20ED%20then%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20Mr%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20AAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20had%20earlier%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20several%20leaders%20of%20her%20party%20and%20was%20trying%20to%20poach%20them%20using%20the%20carrot%20and%20stick%20method.%20She%20and%20a%20few%20others%20were%20approached%20by%20the%20party%2C%20Atishi%20had%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20filed%20a%20defamation%20suit%20against%20her%20over%20the%20claim%20and%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20has%20sent%20a%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Anand%20is%20the%20first%20leader%20of%20AAP%20to%20quit%20with%20a%20public%20allegation%20of%20corruption%20since%20the%20central%20agencies%20started%C2%A0%20a%20series%20of%20arrests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20his%20former%20deputy%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20senior%20leader%20Satyender%20Jain%20are%20in%20jail.%20Only%20one%20leader%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712755800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fv219irn8_saurabh-bharadwaj_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-bjp-said-he-was-corrupt-aap-on-raj-kumar-anand-minister-who-quit-5413492%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi's%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20said%20its%20minister%2C%20Raj%20Kumar%20Anand%2C%20who%20stepped%20down%20today%20accusing%20the%20party%20of%20corruption%2C%20was%20under%20pressure%20from%20investigative%20agencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-bjp-said-he-was-corrupt-aap-on-raj-kumar-anand-minister-who-quit-5413492%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-bjp-said-he-was-corrupt-aap-on-raj-kumar-anand-minister-who-quit-5413492%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-bjp-said-he-was-corrupt-aap-on-raj-kumar-anand-minister-who-quit-5413492%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBSE%20To%20Introduce%20Pilot%20For%20National%20Credit%20Framework%20For%20Classes%206%2C%209%2C%2011%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20is%20set%20to%20introduce%20a%20pilot%20of%20the%20National%20Credit%20Framework%20(NCrF)%20for%20classes%206%2C%209%2C%20and%2011%20from%20the%202024-25%20academic%20session.%20All%20affiliated%20schools%20have%20been%20invited%20by%20the%20board%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CBSE%20developed%20and%20circulated%20draft%20NCrF%20implementation%20guidelines%2C%20discussed%20them%20in%20multiple%20workshops%2C%20and%20received%20approval%20from%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Education.%20To%20further%20test%2C%20refine%2C%20and%20assess%20their%20effectiveness%20in%20real-world%20contexts%2C%20a%20pilot%20implementation%20of%20these%20guidelines%20has%20been%20planned%20in%20schools%20affiliated%20to%20CBSE%20in%20classes%206%2C%209%2C%20and%2011%2C%20with%20effect%20from%20session%202024-2025%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20heads%20of%20all%20the%20institutions%20affiliated%20with%20CBSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrincipals%20of%20interested%20schools%20for%20this%20pilot%20programme%20are%20requested%20to%20share%20their%20contact%20details%20through%20this%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScBihps-Gy0pJynqJwxpy_FtCOW6vnXxfGiGvK0qdXse4UL9g%2Fviewform%5C%22%3E%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20earn%20credits%20through%20various%20activities%20such%20as%20classroom%20instruction%2C%20laboratory%20work%2C%20projects%2C%20sports%2C%20performing%20arts%2C%20NCC%2C%20social%20work%2C%20vocational%20education%2C%20and%20experiential%20learning%2C%20including%20relevant%20professional%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20government%20introduced%20the%20National%20Credit%20Framework%20(NCrF)%20as%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%2C%20aimed%20at%20integrating%20school%2C%20higher%2C%20and%20vocational%20education%2C%20enabling%20students%20to%20accrue%20credits%20from%20pre-primary%20to%20PhD%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20formulated%20draft%20guidelines%20to%20execute%20the%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20close%20the%20gap%20in%20achievement%20of%20learning%20outcomes%20by%20shifting%20the%20classroom%20education%20to%20competency%20and%20learning%20outcome-based%20education%20and%20learning.%20The%20assessment%20is%20thus%20mandatory%20for%20earning%20credits%20for%20all%20types%20of%20learning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20credits%20earned%20shall%20be%20deposited%20in%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credit%20(ABC)%20of%20a%20student%20which%20will%20be%20linked%20with%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20and%20DigiLocker%20of%20the%20student%2C%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712755080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fildclon_school-students_625x300_17_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcbse-to-introduce-pilot-for-national-credit-framework-for-classes-6-9-and-11-5413759%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22National%20Credit%20Framework%20(NCrF)%20shall%20be%20introduced%20in%20CBSE%20Schools%20on%20a%20pilot%20basis%20in%20classes%206%2C%209%20and%2011%20from%20the%20academic%20session%202024-2025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcbse-to-introduce-pilot-for-national-credit-framework-for-classes-6-9-and-11-5413759%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcbse-to-introduce-pilot-for-national-credit-framework-for-classes-6-9-and-11-5413759%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcbse-to-introduce-pilot-for-national-credit-framework-for-classes-6-9-and-11-5413759%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infosys%20tie-up%20with%20Intel%2C%20to%20train%20its%20employees%20on%20AI%20portfolio%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712754859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109199929%2Cimgsize-8204.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Finfosys-expands-tie-up-with-intel-to-train-its-employees-on-companys-ai-portfolio%2Farticleshow%2F109199936.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infosys%20and%20Intel%20collaborate%20to%20accelerate%20AI%20journeys%20by%20integrating%20Gen%20AI%20and%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20Processors.%20The%20partnership%20aims%20to%20provide%20competitive%20TCO%20and%20time-to-value%20AI%20solutions%20while%20supporting%20ISVs%20and%20an%20open%20AI%20software%20ecosystem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Finfosys-expands-tie-up-with-intel-to-train-its-employees-on-companys-ai-portfolio%2Farticleshow%2F109199936.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tissue%20Sample%20Moved%2037%20Km%20In%2020%20Min%2C%20Mid-Surgery%2C%20For%20Cancer%20Testing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research's%20(ICMR)%20trial%20run%2C%20a%20tissue%20sample%20was%20transported%20mid-surgery%20from%20a%20peripheral%20hospital%20in%20Karnataka%20for%20advanced%20pathological%20testing%20at%20a%20tertiary%20setting%20to%20decide%20if%20the%20resected%20tissue%20was%20cancerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20continuance%20with%20the%20national%20mission%20of%20expanding%20the%20drone%20ecosystem%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20ICMR%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20trial%20run%20of%20transporting%20onco-pathological%20samples%20by%20drones%20under%20its%20i-Drone%20initiative%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20efficiently%20transported%20intraoperative%20surgical%20biospecimens%20surgically%20excised%20from%20the%20patient%20from%20Dr%20TMA%20Pai%20Hospital%2C%20Karkala%20to%20Kasturba%20Medical%20College%2C%20Manipal%20Academy%20of%20Higher%20Education%20Manipal%20(tertiary%20care%20hospital)%2C%20covering%20a%20distance%20of%20approximately%2037%20km%20in%2015-20%20minutes%2C%20which%20takes%20around%2050-60%20minutes%20by%20road%2C%20an%20official%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20arrival%2C%20the%20sample%20was%20promptly%20analysed%2C%20and%20the%20report%20was%20electronically%20conveyed%20back%20to%20the%20peripheral%20hospital.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20surgeon%20proceeded%20with%20the%20surgery%20based%20on%20the%20received%20report%2C%20it%20said.%20The%20trial%20run%20as%20part%20of%20a%20validation%20study%20has%20been%20undertaken%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20country%20by%20the%20collaborative%20efforts%20of%20ICMR%2C%20Kasturba%20Medical%20College%20(KMC)%20and%20Dr%20TMA%20PAI%20Rotary%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrones%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20agriculture%2C%20defence%2C%20disaster%20relief%20and%20healthcare%2C%20especially%20during%20emergency%20situations%20by%20enabling%20rapid%20delivery%20of%20vaccines%2C%20medications%2C%20and%20vital%20supplies%20to%20remote%20and%20inaccessible%20areas%2C%20the%20statement%20stated.%20The%20ICMR%20along%20with%20Kasturba%20Medical%20College%20is%20currently%20conducting%20a%20feasibility%20study%20in%20Manipal%2C%20Karnataka.%20The%20study%20aims%20to%20evaluate%20the%20potential%20use%20of%20aerial%20transportation%20systems%20(drones)%2C%20to%20transport%20items%20such%20as%20pathology%20samples%20from%20secondary%20healthcare%20facilities%20to%20tertiary-level%20hospitals%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E(1%2F2)%20Next%20milestone%20achieved%20in%20healthcare%20delivery%20via%20drone!%20Tissue%20sample%20transported%20mid-surgery%20from%20a%20peripheral%20hospital%20for%20Advanced%20pathological%20testing%20at%20tertiary%20setting%20for%20deciding%20if%20the%20resected%20tissue%20is%20cancerous%20or%20not.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMoHFW_INDIA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MoHFW_INDIA%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhbFfjrPAD4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FhbFfjrPAD4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ICMR%20(%40ICMRDELHI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FICMRDELHI%2Fstatus%2F1777938278471319592%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransporting%20samples%20for%20intraoperative%20decision-making%20in%20remote%20areas%20hasn't%20been%20extensively%20explored%20or%20documented%20within%20the%20Indian%20context%20due%20to%20limited%20data%20on%20feasibility%2C%20utility%2C%20and%20cost-effectiveness.%20The%20ongoing%20research%20in%20Manipal%20aims%20to%20address%20this%20gap%20by%20documenting%20the%20procedures%20for%20quick%20transportation%20of%20intraoperative%20samples%20using%20drones%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20innovative%20approach%20could%20potentially%20connect%20secondary%20care%20centres%20with%20limited%20resources%20to%20tertiary%20care%20facilities%20with%20advanced%20diagnostics%2C%20facilitating%20immediate%20access%20during%20surgical%20procedures.%20Ultimately%2C%20this%20initiative%20could%20streamline%20complex%20surgeries%2C%20overcoming%20geographical%20barriers%20and%20improving%20access%20to%20specialized%20care%20in%20peripheral%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICMR%20has%20been%20a%20pioneer%20in%20using%20drones%20for%20healthcare%20purposes%20and%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20delivery%20of%20medical%20supplies%2C%20vaccines%2C%20and%20medicines%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Manipur%20and%20Nagaland%2C%20blood%20bag%20delivery%20in%20Delhi%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20under%20its%20i-DRONE%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20event%2C%20Dr%20Rajiv%20Bahl%2C%20Secretary%20of%20Department%20of%20Health%20Research%20(DHR)%20and%20Director%20General%2C%20ICMR%20emphasized%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20'i-DRONE'%20initiative%20was%20initially%20utilized%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20by%20ICMR%20for%20distributing%20vaccines%20to%20inaccessible%20areas.%20Last%20year%2C%20we%20successfully%20conducted%20trials%20for%20delivering%20blood%20and%20blood-related%20products%2C%20which%20require%20low-temperature%20storage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20in%20another%20study%2C%20we%20transported%20medications%20and%20diagnostic%20samples%20to%20subzero%20temperature%20areas%20and%20challenging%20regions%20with%20altitudes%20exceeding%2012%2C000%20feet%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20In%20this%20ongoing%20study%2C%20our%20focus%20extends%20beyond%20delivering%20pathological%20specimens%3B%20we%20aim%20to%20enhance%20patient%20compliance%20and%20alleviate%20the%20burden%20on%20tertiary%20care%20hospitals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Atul%20Goel%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%20(DGHS)%2C%20expressed%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20study%20holds%20significant%20relevance%20for%20the%20Indian%20context.%20The%20utilization%20of%20drones%20for%20delivering%20healthcare%20essentials%20during%20emergencies%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20save%20numerous%20lives.%20It%20can%20serve%20effectively%20in%20challenging%20geographical%20terrains%2C%20benefiting%20the%20Indian%20population%2C%20while%20also%20bolstering%20India's%20healthcare%20infrastructure.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712754360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fvhcresu8_icmr_625x300_10_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ficmr-trial-run-tissue-sample-transported-mid-surgery-for-advanced-pathological-testing-5413484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ICMR%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20trial%20run%20of%20transporting%20onco-pathological%20samples%20by%20drones%20under%20its%20i-Drone%20initiative.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ficmr-trial-run-tissue-sample-transported-mid-surgery-for-advanced-pathological-testing-5413484%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ficmr-trial-run-tissue-sample-transported-mid-surgery-for-advanced-pathological-testing-5413484%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ficmr-trial-run-tissue-sample-transported-mid-surgery-for-advanced-pathological-testing-5413484%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Jailed%20For%20Stealing%20Diary%20Belonging%20To%20Joe%20Biden's%20Daughter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20from%20Florida%2C%20United%20States%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20a%20month%20in%20prison%20after%20she%20stole%20the%20diary%20of%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20daughter%20and%20sold%20it%20to%20a%20conservative%20advocacy%20group%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fcrime%2Fashley-biden-diary-stolen-sentencing-b2526044.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20US%20district%20judge%20ruled%20that%20the%2041-year-old%20would%20face%20jail%20time%20and%20three%20months%20of%20home%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20stole%20Ashley%20Biden's%20diary%20and%20other%20belongings%20from%20a%20friend's%20Florida%20house%20in%202020.%20The%20President's%20daughter%20had%20kept%20them%20at%20home%20for%20safekeeping.%20Harris%20then%20accepted%20%2420%2C000%20from%20Project%20Veritas%2C%20a%20far-right%20organisation%2C%20for%20selling%20the%20journal.%20In%202022%2C%20she%20entered%20a%20guilty%20plea%20to%20a%20charge%20of%20conspiring%20to%20transfer%20stolen%20goods%20across%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20plea%2C%20Harris%20missed%20many%20sentencing%20sessions.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20she%20expressed%20her%20regret%20to%20the%20court%20and%20said%20she%20was%20busy%20caring%20for%20her%20two%20children.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20believe%20I%20am%20above%20the%20law.%20I'm%20a%20survivor%20of%20long-term%20domestic%20abuse%20and%20sexual%20trauma%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2041-year-old%20was%20charged%20along%20with%20Robert%20Kurlander%2C%20who%20helped%20her%20with%20selling%20the%20diary.%20Initially%2C%20the%20two%20attempted%20to%20negotiate%20a%20settlement%20with%20a%20representative%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%202020%20re-election%20campaign.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20campaign%20backed%20out%2C%20the%20representative%20advised%20them%20to%20give%20the%20diary%20and%20other%20materials%20to%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI).%20Later%2C%20they%20sold%20it%20to%20Project%20Veritas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJames%20O'Keefe%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Project%20Veritas%2C%20and%20two%20colleagues%20had%20their%20houses%20searched%20by%20FBI%20officials%20as%20part%20of%20their%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegations.%20Project%20Veritas%20and%20Mr%20O'Keefe%20have%20not%20been%20charged%20in%20this%20case.%20Project%20Veritas%20withheld%20the%20journals%2C%20which%20allegedly%20documented%20Ms%20Biden's%20recovery%20journey%20from%20drug%20abuse.%20However%2C%20the%20documents%20were%20published%20by%20a%20different%20outlet%20with%20minor%20redactions%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68776262%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20diary%20was%20later%20handed%20over%20to%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20by%20Project%20Veritas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStealing%20personal%20belongings%20of%20a%20candidate's%20family%20member%2C%20and%20selling%20them%20to%20an%20organisation%20to%20exploit%20them%20for%20political%20gain%2C%20was%20wrong%20and%20illegal%20no%20matter%20the%20political%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prosecutors%20wrote%20in%20the%20sentencing%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712753160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fr89cu7r8_joe-biden-ashley-biden_625x300_10_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-jailed-for-stealing-diary-belonging-to-joe-bidens-daughter-5413628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2041-year-old%20was%20charged%20along%20with%20Robert%20Kurlander%2C%20who%20helped%20her%20with%20selling%20the%20diary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-jailed-for-stealing-diary-belonging-to-joe-bidens-daughter-5413628%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-jailed-for-stealing-diary-belonging-to-joe-bidens-daughter-5413628%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-jailed-for-stealing-diary-belonging-to-joe-bidens-daughter-5413628%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20China%20top%20buyers%20of%20Russ