%20are%20available%20for%20future%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQuest%20of%20a%20farm%20boy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20childhood%2C%20Neelam%20recalls%20being%20compelled%20to%20study%20due%20to%20societal%20pressure.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20a%20farm%20boy!%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20agriculture%20like%20my%20father.%20He%20was%20a%20medical%20doctor%20by%20profession%20but%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20farm%20in%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%20But%20sadly%2C%20Neelam%E2%80%99s%20father%20passed%20away%20from%20a%20stroke%20while%20Neelam%20was%20studying%20in%20Class%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20completing%20Class%2012%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20graduation%20in%20arts%20from%20an%20open%20school.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20so%20disinterested%20that%20I%20neglected%20to%20submit%20assignments%20required%20to%20complete%20the%20degree%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20Pabhoi%20village%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Heirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett