st%2010%20years%2C%20Diganata%20Bora%20has%20been%20cultivating%20vegetables%20using%20such%20heirloom%20seeds%20on%20his%20two-acre%20farm%20in%20Paschim%20Manjiri%20village%20of%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20hybrid%20varieties%2C%20we%20get%20good%20yield%20using%20heirloom%20ones.%20In%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5B0.33%20acre%5D%2C%20we%20now%20get%206-7%20quintals%20of%20vegetables%20over%202-2.5%20quintals.%20Additionally%2C%20our%20input%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%20as%20we%20use%20readily%20available%20cow%20dung%20as%20fertiliser.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20have%20decided%20to%20switch%3B%20now%20our%20soil%20fertility%20has%20also%20improved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Diganata%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20concludes%2C%20%E2%80%9CBack%20when%20I%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F176277%2Fkarnataka-bengaluru-organic-farming-native-seeds-woman%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%20no%20resources%20available%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20from.%20Now%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20to%20have%20created%20a%20helpful%20platform%20for%20other%20farmers.%20When%20I%20visit%20their%20fields%2C%20I%20feel%20great%20to%20see%20the%20joy%20on%20their%20faces.%20By%20cultivating%20their%20own%20organic%20seeds%20and%20crops%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20made%20agriculture%20economically%20viable%20in%20our%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Neelam%20Dutta.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712239080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346317%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alarmed%20by%20the%20effect%20of%20climate%20change%20on%20food%20security%2C%20Assam-based%20Neelam%20Dutta%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20safeguard%20heirloom%20seeds.%20Under%20his%20venture%20%E2%80%98Pabhoi%20Greens%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20over%2024%2C000%20farmers%20in%20Northeast%20India%20in%20organic%20cultivation%20and%20seed%20preservation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346317%2Fassam-organic-farmer-neelam-dutta-conserves-climate-resilient-heirloom-seeds-pabhoi-greens-northeast%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Selling%20Lemonade%20To%20Building%20a%20108-YO%20Dairy%20Empire%3A%20Journey%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Loved%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDecades%20ago%2C%20if%20anyone%20were%20to%20ask%20veteran%20Bollywood%20actress%20Mumtaz%20where%20she%20was%20heading%20on%20a%20hot%20summer%20afternoon%2C%20she%E2%80%99d%20reply%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%2C%20of%20course%E2%80%9D.%20Through%20the%20years%2C%20her%20answer%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20changed.%20Today%2C%20Mumtaz%20is%20not%20the%20only%20name%20on%20the%20influential%20guest%20list.%20Also%20featured%20are%20actors%20Jim%20Sarbh%20and%20Boman%20Irani.%20For%20a%20business%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295229%2Ftaj-icecream-mumbai-eatery-loved-by-madhubala-makes-natural-icecream-in-wooden-barrels%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20draw%20for%20celebrities%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ambanis%2C%20the%20Birlas%2C%20and%20the%20Tatas%2C%20they%20must%20be%20doing%20something%20right!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20anyone%20will%20affirm%2C%20a%20menu%20boasting%20scrumptious%20sweets%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20draw%20of%20this%20dairy%20venture%20located%20off%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Princess%20Street.%20It%20is%20its%20century-old%20charm%20and%20the%20recipe%20that%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20generations%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20where%20the%20magic%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20wondering%20why%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20has%20continued%20to%20see%20an%20unwavering%20customer%20base%20for%20over%20108%20years%20now%2C%20the%20proof%20is%20literally%20and%20metaphorically%20in%20the%20pudding.%20The%20history%20of%20the%20business%20ties%20back%20to%20when%20a%20young%20boy%20of%2016%20began%20delivering%20milk%20cans%20to%20homes%20around%20Kalbadevi%20(an%20old%20neighbourhood%20in%20Mumbai).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20Nariman%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20first%20choice%20of%20a%20job.%20Circumstances%20led%20him%20to%20it%2C%20and%20ambition%20paved%20the%20way%20to%20success.%20Since%201916%2C%20when%20Ardeshir%20sold%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327249%2Fkota-engineer-runs-sustainable-dairy-farm-saves-on-electricy-bills-gau-organics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20can%20of%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20seen%20its%20trajectory%20of%20ups%20interspersed%20with%20downs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20fourth%20generation%20settles%20down%20to%20chat%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20they%20say%20challenges%20are%20a%20part%20of%20any%20business.%20What%20sets%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20apart%2C%20however%2C%20is%20its%20recipe%20for%20dealing%20with%20adversity.%20The%20women%20and%20children%20have%20never%20shied%20away%20from%20steering%20the%20legacy%20forward%20when%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20cousins%20laugh%20over%20childhood%20anecdotes%2C%20stories%20of%20taking%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20family%20legacy%20and%20nostalgic%20memories%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20the%20dairy%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20just%20a%20family%20business%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20loved%20member%20that%20has%20had%20its%20own%20seat%20at%20the%20family%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D