0and%20got%20the%20whole%20place%20to%20look%20amazing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20the%20activity%20was%20a%20success%20then%2C%20just%20like%20the%20revamped%20interiors%20are%20now.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20siblings%20cherish%20these%20family%20activities%2C%20the%20others%20hold%20fond%20memories%20involving%20the%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvana%20Mistry%20(36)%20who%20now%20heads%20operations%20at%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20recalls%20hours%20spent%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekarkhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(factory)%20when%20she%20was%20little.%20Her%20ears%20would%20perk%20up%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340041%2Fentrepreneur-save-family-business-harshit-tanay-agrawal-pistabarfi-cloud-kitchen-janta-dairy-sweets-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esizzle%20of%20the%20sweets%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20prepared%20and%20her%20eyes%20would%20longingly%20watch%20the%20fresh%20piles%20of%20%3Cem%3Esutarfeni%20%3C%2Fem%3E(an%20Indian%20speciality%20made%20with%20flour%20roasted%20in%20ghee%20and%20blended%20with%20melted%20sugar)%2C%20eagerly%20awaiting%20her%20turn%20to%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTill%20today%20when%20I%20see%20%3Cem%3Ejalebis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20takes%20me%20back%20to%20those%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20fondly%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4fx9L-otJ6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4fx9L-otJ6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E