s%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E(traditional%20Indian%20ice%20cream).%20%E2%80%9CThey%20always%20ring%20a%20bell%20with%20me.%20The%20cool%20creamy%20and%20mouthwatering%20taste%20is%20amazing.%20It%20melts%20in%20the%20plate%20and%20even%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebasundi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(thickened%20milk)%20that%20comes%20up%20is%20just%20amazing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revamped%20Parsi%20dairy%20Farm%20also%20boasts%20a%20%E2%80%98Great%20Indian%20Toffee%20Wonderland%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20has%20an%20array%20of%20delicious%20sweets%20(earlier%20known%20as%20milk%20drops).%20Growing%20up%20these%20were%20Bakhtyar%E2%80%99s%20favourites%20and%20now%20he%20enjoys%20the%20fudge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20family%20prides%20themselves%20on%20their%20legacy%2C%20they%20mention%20their%20mothers%20who%20were%20founding%20pillars%20of%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20took%20the%20reigns%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20common%20for%20women%20to%20work.%20Our%20fathers%20also%20were%20extremely%20supportive%20of%20them%20doing%20this%3B%20encouraging%20them%20and%20helping%20them%20in%20whatever%20way%20that%20was%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Zeenia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20amazing%20about%20having%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337104%2Feasy-recipe-for-gajar-ka-halwa-history-winter-dessert%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20legacy%20%3C%2Fa%3Elike%20this%2C%20says%20Parvana%2C%20is%20that%20most%20of%20the%20sweets%20are%20older%20than%20her.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20mind%20you%2C%20they%20are%20still%20made%20with%20the%20same%20recipe%20as%20they%20were.%20We%20make%20our%20sweets%20with%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20delight%2C%20precision%2C%20and%20tradition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20the%20years%20the%20dairy%20has%20seen%20guests%20the%20likes%20of%20Mumtaz%2C%20Jim%20Sarbh%2C%20Boman%20Irani%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345658%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20the%20years%20the%20dairy%20has%20seen%20guests%20the%20likes%20of%20Mumtaz%2C%20Jim%20Sarbh%2C%20Boman%20Irani%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Zeenia%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20old%20machinery%20such%20as%20the%20Gerber%2C%20the%20weighing%20scale%2C%20and%20the%20pasteuriser%20have%20still%20been%20preserved%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20htt